Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20Met%20Police%2C%20which%20serves%20the%20Greater%20London%20area%2C%20the%20force%20said%20there%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bpockets%20of%20disorder%20and%20some%20instances%20of%20hate%20speech%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20demonstrations%20and%20five%20officers%20suffered%20minor%20injuries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficers%20also%20reviewed%20a%20video%20from%20a%20Hizb%20ut-Tahrir%20protest%20in%20which%20a%20man%20can%20be%20seen%20chanting%20%26quot%3Bjihad%2C%20jihad%26quot%3B%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20word%20has%20a%20number%20of%20meanings%20but%20we%20know%20the%20public%20will%20most%20commonly%20associate%20it%20with%20terrorism.%20Specialist%20officers%20have%20assessed%20the%20video%20and%20have%20not%20identified%20any%20offences%20arising%20from%20the%20specific%20clip%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENearly%201%2C00%2C000%20people%20gathered%20at%20the%20demonstrations%20across%20London%20on%20Saturday%20and%20a%20few%20thousand%20across%20the%20other%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESunak%20was%20in%20Israel%20last%20week%2C%20standing%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Israel%20and%20the%20people.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20here%20to%20express%20my%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Israeli%20people.%20You%20have%20suffered%20an%20unspeakable%2C%20horrific%20act%20of%20terrorism%20and%20I%20want%20you%20to%20know%20that%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20and%20I%20stand%20with%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20upon%20his%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%26quot%3B%20supports%20Israel's%20%26quot%3Bright%20to%20defend%20itself%20and%20to%20go%20after%20Hamas%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20Sunak%20met%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20and%2C%20addressing%20a%20joint%20conference%20with%20Netanyahu%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20you%20are%20taking%20every%20precaution%20to%20not%20harm%20civilians%2C%20unlike%20the%20Hamas.%20Thank%20you%20for%20the%20evacuation%20of%20British%20citizens.%20We%20recognise%20Palestinians%20are%20the%20victims%20of%20Hamas%20too.%20Glad%20you%20opened%20areas%20for%20humanitarian%20aid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698140040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fpglbmrek_rishi-sunak-1200_625x300_30_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwont-tolerate-uk-pm-rishi-sunak-on-jihad-chants-at-pro-palestine-rallies-4509248%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22British%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20said%20anti-semitism%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated%20in%20the%20UK%20days%20after%20London%20and%20other%20cities%20saw%20a%20series%20of%20protests%20across%20on%20Saturday%20over%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20and%20as%20a%20show%20of%20solidarity%20with%20Palestinians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwont-tolerate-uk-pm-rishi-sunak-on-jihad-chants-at-pro-palestine-rallies-4509248%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwont-tolerate-uk-pm-rishi-sunak-on-jihad-chants-at-pro-palestine-rallies-4509248%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwont-tolerate-uk-pm-rishi-sunak-on-jihad-chants-at-pro-palestine-rallies-4509248%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man's%20Best%20Friend%20Or%20Ferocious%20Foe%3A%20Explaining%20India's%20Stray%20Dog%20Problem%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20of%20a%20prominent%20businessman%2C%20reportedly%20after%20a%20fall%20while%20running%20from%20stray%20dogs%2C%20has%20reignited%20the%20discussion%20on%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20contain%20the%20stray%20dog%20menace%20on%20Indian%20streets%20that%20has%20claimed%20several%20lives%2C%20including%20that%20of%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EForty-nine-year-old%20Parag%20Desai%2C%20an%20executive%20director%20with%20Wagh%20Bakri%20Tea%20Group%20died%20of%20a%20brain%20hemorrhage%20yesterday.%20A%20statement%20from%20the%20hospital%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20stated%20that%20the%20patient%20fell%20down%20after%20being%20chased%20by%20dogs%20but%20apparently%2C%20there%20were%20no%20dog%20bite%20marks%20on%20his%20body.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20debate%20on%20stronger%20action%20against%20stray%20dogs%20resumed%20on%20social%20media.%20Many%20cited%20examples%20of%20the%20Netherlands%20and%20the%20US%20and%20how%20they%20have%20addressed%20the%20stray%20dog%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Has%20The%20Netherlands%20Done%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Netherlands%20claims%20to%20have%20zero%20stray%20dogs.%20It%20acheived%20this%20through%20a%20CNVR%20programme%20-%20Collect%2C%20Neuter%2C%20Vaccinate%2C%20and%20Return.%20Many%20local%20bodies%20have%20also%20spiked%20taxes%20for%20owning%20store-bought%20dogs%20to%20incentivise%20adopting%20from%20animal%20shelters.%20Dutch%20laws%20mandate%20that%20every%20dog%20has%20to%20be%20neutered%20or%20spayed.%20These%20procedures%20are%20funded%20by%20the%20government.%20There%20are%20fines%20for%20cruelty%20against%20dogs%20and%20also%20a%20special%20force%20to%20act%20in%20such%20cases.%20Those%20with%20concerns%20over%20an%20animal%20can%20contact%20the%20special%20force.%20There%20is%20a%20large%20number%20of%20animal%20shelters%20to%20house%20such%20animals.%20All%20these%20shelters%20are%20%26quot%3Bno-kill%26quot%3B%20-%20meaning%20euthanasia%20is%20not%20an%20option.%20A%20huge%20section%20of%20the%20Dutch%20population%20owns%20a%20dog%2C%20and%20none%20are%20on%20the%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20US%20Approach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20too%20has%20a%20system%20that%20prevents%20the%20stray%20dogs%20problem.%20Stray%20animals%20are%20accommodated%20into%20animal%20shelters%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%20no-kill%20shelters.%20A%20no-kill%20animal%20shelter%20is%20one%20where%20animals%20are%20not%20killed%20unless%20they%20are%20terminally%20ill.%20The%20US%2C%20however%2C%20is%20now%20facing%20a%20problem%20--%20space%20crunch%20in%20animal%20shelters.%20This%20is%20forcing%20to%20euthanise%20lakhs%20of%20dogs%20annually.%20Some%20reports%20had%20claimed%20financial%20difficulties%20and%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20had%20forced%20many%20owners%20to%20abandon%20pets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20India%20Problem%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20currently%20accounts%20for%2036%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20world's%20rabies%20deaths%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization.%20At%20least%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20these%20victims%20are%20under%20the%20age%20of%2015.%20Visuals%20of%20children%20being%20attacked%20by%20stray%20dogs%20often%20surface%20on%20social%20media%2C%20triggering%20demands%20for%20immediate%20steps%20to%20curb%20the%20stray%20dog%20problem.%20Dogbites%20in%20children%20are%20often%20unreported%20because%20they%20are%20afraid%20of%20speaking%20out.%20This%20September%2C%20a%2014-year-old%20boy%20died%20of%20rabies%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Ghaziabad.%20Shahvaz%20was%20bitten%20by%20his%20neighbour's%20dog%20about%20two%20months%20back%2C%20but%20did%20not%20tell%20this%20at%20home%20out%20of%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPublic%20Anger%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20horrifying%20videos%20of%20dog%20bite%20incidents%20emerging%20on%20social%20media%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20call%20to%20take%20strong%20steps%20have%20grown%20louder.%20Reports%20of%20a%20face-off%20between%20animal%20lovers%20and%20those%20opposing%20their%20activities%20in%20public%20spaces%20have%20often%20come%20to%20the%20fore.%20Pet%20owners%2C%20too%2C%20have%20faced%20opposition%20to%20dogs%20using%20common%20facilities%20such%20as%20lift%20following%20incidents%20of%20dog%20bites.%20Among%20the%20solutions%20suggested%20for%20stray%20dog%20menace%20is%20euthanasia%20and%20enhanced%20action%20by%20local%20bodies%20to%20house%20strays%20in%20animal%20shelters.%20The%20public%20anger%20against%20stray%20dogs%20has%20led%20to%20several%20incidents%20of%20animal%20cruelty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Do%20Laws%20Say%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%202001%2C%20municipal%20authorities%20could%20euthanise%20stray%20dogs%20to%20keep%20public%20places%20safe.%20In%202001%20came%20the%20Animal%20Birth%20Control%20(Dogs)%20Rules.%20These%20rules%20created%20a%20separate%20catrgory%20called%20%26quot%3Bstreet%20dogs%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20they%20should%20be%20sterilized%20and%20immunised%20by%20%26quot%3Bparticipation%20of%20animal%20welfare%20organizations%2C%20private%20individuals%20and%20the%20local%20authority%26quot%3B.%20These%20rules%20were%20silent%20on%20euthanising%20stray%20dogs%20except%20those%20%26quot%3Bincurably%20ill%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bmortally%20wounded%26quot%3B.%20It%20also%20said%20dogs%20caught%20for%20sterlisation%20and%20vaccination%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Breleased%20in%20the%20same%20area%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Are%20The%20Challenges%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20solution%20to%20the%20stray%20dog%20problem%20in%20India%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20steps%20taken%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20faces%20many%20challenges.%20The%20biggest%20among%20them%20is%20the%20funds%20crunch.%20Sterlization%20of%20dogs%20is%20expensive%20and%20cash-strapped%20municipal%20bodies%20often%20put%20it%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20their%20priority%20list.%20To%20shift%20dogs%20to%20animal%20shelters%20would%20require%20huge%20investment%20in%20building%20such%20shelters.%20The%20less-desirable%20euthanasia%20solution%2C%20advocated%20by%20some%20voices%2C%20faces%20other%20hurdles.%20Religious%20beliefs%20in%20India%20bar%20cruelty%20towards%20animals%20and%20as%20a%20society%2C%20there%20is%20an%20uneasiness%20over%20accepting%20a%20solution%20such%20as%20killing%20an%20animal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20The%20Way%20Out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20lasting%20solution%20to%20the%20stray%20dog%20problem%20would%20require%20far-sighted%20planning%2C%20significant%20government%20spending%20and%20public%20awareness%20exercises%20to%20sensitise%20people%20on%20animal%20cruelty.%20For%20a%20developing%20country%20still%20battling%20poverty%20in%20a%20large%20section%20its%20population%2C%20funding%20for%20animal%20shelters%20and%20care%20remains%20a%20tall%20challenge.%20However%2C%20choosing%20an%20option%20to%20euthanise%20stray%20animals%20may%20lead%20to%20cases%20of%20misuse%20and%20animal%20cruelty.%20Petitions%20by%20a%20Kerala%20local%20body%2C%20seeking%20permission%20to%20cull%20stray%20dogs%2C%20is%20now%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20court%20last%20month%20said%20it%20will%20issue%20strong%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698139980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fe6u97c98_stray-dogs-generic_625x300_18_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstray-dogs-stray-dog-menace-mans-best-friend-or-ferocious-foe-explaining-indias-stray-dog-problem-4509443%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20death%20of%20a%20prominent%20businessman%2C%20reportedly%20after%20a%20fall%20while%20running%20from%20stray%20dogs%2C%20has%20reignited%20the%20discussion%20on%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20contain%20the%20stray%20dog%20menace%20on%20Indian%20streets%20that%20has%20claimed%20several%20lives%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstray-dogs-stray-dog-menace-mans-best-friend-or-ferocious-foe-explaining-indias-stray-dog-problem-4509443%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstray-dogs-stray-dog-menace-mans-best-friend-or-feroci