ve-managed-to-only-scratch-the-surface-when-it-comes-to-depicting-it-on-screen-karan-hariharan%2Farticleshow%2F104671027.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224%20US%20Citizens%20Steal%20Dinosaur%20Bones%20Worth%20%241%20Million%2C%20Sell%20It%20To%20China%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFour%20people%20in%20the%20United%20States%20have%20been%20charged%20for%20purchasing%20and%20reselling%20%26quot%3Bpaleontological%20resources%26quot%3B%20worth%20over%20%241%20million%2C%20including%20dinosaur%20bones%20that%20were%20exported%20to%20China%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2F4-charged-illegal-sale-dinosaur-bones-shipped-china-rcna121488%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20Vint%20Wade%20and%20Donna%20Wade%2C%20lived%20in%20Utah.%20Both%20are%20aged%2065%20and%2067%20respectively.%20The%20other%20two%2C%20Steven%20Willing%2C%2067%20and%20Jordan%20Willing%2C%2040%2C%20are%20from%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20Oregon.%20Although%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20Wades%20remains%20unknown%2C%20the%20Willings%20are%20a%20father-and-son%20duo.%20All%20of%20them%20have%20committed%20multiple%20felonies%20and%20violated%20the%20Paleontological%20Resources%20Preservation%20Act%2C%20as%20per%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-ut%2Fpr%2Fover-1m-worth-dinosaur-bones-allegedly-stolen-utah-shipped-china-profit%5C%22%3EUS%20Attorney's%20Office%20for%20the%20District%20of%20Utah%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BA%20federal%20grand%20jury%20in%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20returned%20a%2013-count%20indictment%20charging%20four%20people%20for%20allegedly%20purchasing%20and%20selling%20over%20%241M%20in%20paleontological%20resources.%20The%20dollar%20amount%20represents%20150%2C000%20pounds%20of%20paleontological%20resources%2C%20including%20dinosaur%20bones%2C%20illegally%20