ently%20promoting%20her%20film%20'Tejas'%2C%20scheduled%20to%20be%20released%20on%20Friday.%20The%20movie%2C%20written%20and%20directed%20by%20Sarvesh%20Mewara%2C%20features%20her%20in%20the%20role%20of%20an%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20pilot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkangana-ranaut-meets-national-security-advisor-ajit-doval-on-a-flight-amid-tejas-promotion%2Farticleshow%2F104670513.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Bizarre%20Currency%20Exchange%20Plot%20Involves%20Occultist%2C%20Djinn%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20unique%20case%20has%20surfaced%20in%20Gwalior%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20involving%20a%20self-proclaimed%20occultist%20who%20asserted%20his%20ability%20to%20use%20a%20djinn's%20power%20to%20swap%20old%20currency%20for%20new%20on%20Dussehra.%20However%2C%20this%20bizarre%20scheme%20took%20an%20unexpected%20turn%20when%20a%20man%20fell%20into%20the%20occultist's%20trap%20and%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20police%20while%20attempting%20to%20transport%20a%20large%20sum%20of%20demonetised%20Rs%20500%20and%20Rs%201000%20notes.%20The%20seized%20old%20currency%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20valued%20at%20Rs%2047%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20initially%20investigated%20the%20angle%20that%20the%20huge%20amount%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20distributed%20among%20villages%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections.%20But%20the%20arrested%20man's%20confession%20spun%20a%20different%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20identified%20as%20Sultan%20Karosiya%2C%20hailing%20from%20Barokhar%20in%20Morena%20district%2C%20explained%20to%20the%20police%20that%20he%20had%20stumbled%20upon%20these%20demonetised%20notes%20in%20a%20garbage%20heap%20approximately%206-7%20months%20before%20the%20demonetization%20policy%20was%20enforced.%20He%20clandestinely%20preserved%20this%20collection%20in%20his%20residence%20without%20disclosing%20it%20to%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESultan%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20been%20informed%20by%20a%20person%20known%20to%20him%20that%2C%20on%20Dussehra%2C%20an%20occultist%20could%20invoke%20a%20djinn%20through%20a%20mystical%20ritual%2C%20and%20the%20djinn%20would%20facilitate%20the%20exchange%20of%20bundles%20of%20old%20notes%20for%20new%20currency.%20To%20facilitate%20this%20exchange%2C%20he%20set%20out%20with%2041%20bundles%20of%20Rs%201000%20notes%20and%2012%20bundles%20of%20Rs%20500%20notes.%20However%2C%20his%20plans%20were%20foiled%20when%20the%20police%20intercepted%20him%20during%20a%20routine%20check.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20police%20also%20arrested%20his%20associate%2C%20Jitendra%20Bhadauria%2C%20and%20initiated%20efforts%20to%20trace%20the%20occultist%20involved%20in%20this%20unusual%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Additional%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Hrishikesh%20Meena%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Crime%20Branch%20had%20received%20a%20tip-off%20that%20an%20individual%20was%20en%20route%20to%20Gwalior%20from%20Morena%20on%20a%20motorcycle%2C%20carrying%20a%20substantial%20sum%20of%20money%20in%20a%20black%20bag.%20In%20response%20to%20this%20information%2C%20the%20Crime%20Branch%20team%20was%20deployed%20at%20the%20place%20mentioned%20by%20the%20informant.%20They%20began%20stopping%20and%20searching%20vehicles%20coming%20and%20going%20from%20the%20area%2C%20eventually%20spotting%20the%20mentioned%20motorcycle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUpon%20interrogation%2C%20the%20individual%20identified%20himself%20as%20a%20resident%20of%20Morena%2C%20near%20the%20Polytechnic%20College.%20When%20questioned%20about%20the%20old%20notes%20found%20in%20his%20bag%2C%20he%20failed%20to%20provide%20a%20satisfactory%20explanation.%20Upon%20counting%2C%20the%20police%20discovered%2041%20bundles%20of%20old%20Rs%201000%20notes%20and%2012%20bundles%20of%20old%20Rs%20500%20