o%20official%20Israeli%20sources%20they%20are%20doing%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20220%20others%2C%20including%20the%20husbands%20of%20both%20the%20freed%20women%2C%20Amiram%20Cooper%2C%2084%2C%20and%20Oded%20Lifshitz%2C%2083%2C%20are%20still%20being%20held%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20Hamas%20said%20the%20two%20elderly%20Israeli%20women%20were%20released%20as%20a%20humanitarian%20gesture.%20In%20Israel%2C%20the%20release%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20Hamas%20effort%20to%20improve%20its%20image%20vis%20a%20vis%20the%20regional%20and%20international%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20interview%20with%20Western%20media%20since%20October%207%2C%20Khaled%20Mashaal%2C%20a%20Hamas%20leader%20living%20in%20Qatar%2C%20suggested%20that%20the%20organization%20will%20release%20all%20civilian%20hostages%20if%20Israel%20stops%20its%20attack%20on%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20them%20stop%20this%20aggression%20and%20you%20will%20find%20the%20mediators%20like%20Qatar%20and%20Egypt%20and%20some%20Arab%20countries%20and%20others%20will%20find%20a%20way%20to%20have%20them%20released%20and%20we'll%20send%20them%20to%20their%20homes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%20isn't%20possible%20while%20Israel's%20air%20offensive%20remains%20intense.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20stop%20the%20random%20bombardments%2C%20the%20total%20destruction%2C%20the%20genocide%20so%20that%20the%20al%20Qassam%20soldiers%20can%20take%20them%20from%20their%20places%20and%20hand%20them%20to%20the%20Red%20Cross%20or%20whoever.%20We%20need%20the%20right%20conditions%20to%20allow%20them%20to%20be%20released%2C%26quot%3B%20Khaled%20Mashaal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20rare%20move%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Intelligence%20community%20on%20Monday%20presented%20previously%20unseen%20raw%20footage%20to%20the%20foreign%20press%20at%20a%20military%20base%20in%20central%20Israel.%20The%20footage%2C%20mainly%20obtained%20from%20the%20GoPro%20bodycam%20cameras%20of%20Hamas%20members%20and%20surveillance%20cameras%2C%20is%20a%20part%20of%20an%20Israeli%20effort%20to%20fight%20what%20is%20described%20as%20Holocaust-like%20denials%20of%20Hamas's%20massacres%20in%20southern%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20videos%20and%20photos%20showed%20murder%2C%20torture%20and%20even%20decapitation%20of%20Israeli%20citizens.%20A%20recording%20of%20a%20phone%20conversation%20also%20reveals%20how%20a%20Hamas%20member%20proudly%20called%20his%20family%20inside%20Gaza%20from%20a%20phone%20he%20had%20stolen%20from%20an%20Israeli%20victim.%20In%20the%20conversation%20the%20Hamas%20member%20can%20be%20heard%20talking%20to%20his%20father.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDad%2C%20I%20killed%2010%20with%20my%20bare%20hands.%20Their%20blood%20is%20on%20my%20hands%2C%20let%20me%20speak%20to%20Mom.%20Please%20be%20proud%20of%20me%2C%20Dad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20keeps%20delaying%20its%20expected%20land%20invasion%20of%20Gaza.%20Although%20the%20army%20is%20ready%2C%20no%20green%20light%20has%20been%20given%20from%20the%20political%20leadership.%20Aryeh%20Deri%2C%20a%20veteran%20Israeli%20politician%20and%20close%20ally%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20explained%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20delay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20over%20two%20weeks%20after%20the%20terrible%20terrorist%20attack%20we%20went%20through.%20We%20must%20tell%20the%20truth%2C%20no%20one%20was%20prepared%20for%20this.%20No%20one%20was%20prepared%20for%20such%20a%20terrible%20disaster%2C%20the%20large%20volumes%20of%20the%20murdered%20and%20kidnapped%2C%20and%20a%20very%20difficult%20struggle%20on%20several%20fronts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAryeh%20Deri%20said%20Israel%20never%20had%20a%20plan%20for%20toppling%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20and%20therefore%20needed%20time%20to%20evolve%20a%20comprehensive%20plan.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BFrom%20that%20moment%20on%2C%20we%20had%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20real%20war%2C%20the%20goal%20of%20which%20is%20agreed%20upon%20by%20all%20is%20that%20Hamas%20does%20not%20remain%20in%20existence%20-%20neither%20from%20a%20governmental%20point%20of%20view%20nor%20from%20a%20military%20point%20of%20view.%20Here%2C%20too%2C%20we%20have%20to%20say%20honestly%2C%20there%20was%20no%20such%20plan.%20It%20is%20being%20prepared%20during%20the%20battle.%20It%20is%20not%20currently%20extant.%20It%20is%20not%20that%20the%20army%20is%20ready%20and%20the%20political%20echelon%20only%20needs%20to%20make%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20diplomatic%20front%2C%20the%20US%20kept%20pushing%20for%20a%20UN%20resolution%20condemning%20Hamas'%20attacks%20and%20backing%20Israel's%20right%20to%20self-defense%20in%20preparation%20for%20Tuesday's%20monthly%20meeting%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20draft%20of%20the%20resolution%2C%20obtained%20by%20AP%2C%20demands%20the%20immediate%20release%20of%20all%20hostages%2C%20urges%20respect%20for%20international%20laws%20on%20conducting%20war%20and%20protecting%20civilians%2C%20urges%20all%20countries%20to%20intensify%20efforts%20to%20prevent%20spillover%2C%20and%20demands%20immediate%20humanitarian%20access%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20spillover%20effect%20of%20the%20Gaza%20conflict%2C%20US%20forces%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20have%20already%20come%20under%20attack%20on%20several%20fronts.%20On%20Monday%2C%20Iran-backed%20militias%20in%20Iraq%20claimed%20they%20attacked%20two%20US%20bases%20in%20eastern%20Syria%2C%20marking%20a%20fourth%20attack%20in%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Islamic%20Resistance%20in%20Iraq%2C%20a%20drone%20attack%20was%20carried%20out%20against%20the%20US%20military%20bases%20near%20the%20Al-Omar%20oil%20field%20in%20Deir%20el-Zour%20province%20and%20in%20al-Shaddadi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20that%20day%20the%20Islamic%20Resistance%20in%20Iraq%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20drone%20attacks%20on%20the%20al-Tanf%20garrison%20near%20the%20Jordanian%20and%20Iraqi%20borders.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20boost%20military%20capabilities%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20US%20has%20dispatched%20several%20military%20advisers%20to%20Israel%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days.%20Among%20them%2C%20according%20to%20Times%20of%20Israel%2C%20is%20Marine%20Corps%20Lieutenant%20General%20James%20Glynn.%20He%20took%20part%20in%20US%20special%20forces%20operations%20against%20Islamic%20State%20in%20Iraq.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20development%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20for%20the%20first%20time%20downed%20a%20drone%20in%20the%20skies%20above%20the%20Haifa%20bay.%20The%20drone%20entered%20Israeli%20territory%20from%20Lebanon%20and%20was%20shot%20down%20minutes%20before%20it%20could%20reach%20the%20city%20of%20Haifa%2C%20a%20major%20Israeli%20city%20with%20a%20population%20of%20approximately%20300%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Israel's%20northern%20border%20with%20Lebanon%2C%20mutual%20attacks%20between%20Hezbollah%20and%20Israel%20continued%20yesterday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20visit%20to%20a%20military%20base%20in%20northern%20Israel%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20warned%20Hezbollah%20against%20escalating%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20tell%20you%20right%20now%20if%20Hezbollah%20will%20decide%20to%20fully%20enter%20the%20war.%20If%20Hezbollah%20decides%20to%20enter%20the%20war%2C%20it%20will%20long%20for%20the%20Second%20Lebanon%20War%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%202006%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20televised%20conversation%20with%20elite%20soldiers%2C%20Netanyahu%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThat%20would%20be%20its%20biggest%20mistake%20ever.%20We%20will%20cripple%20it%20with%20a%20force%20it%20cannot%20even%20imagine%2C%20and%20the%20meaning%20for%20it%20and%20for%20the%20state%20of%20Lebanon%20will%20be%20devastating%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Allan%20Sorensen%20is%20the%20Middle%20East%20correspondent%20for%20the%20Danish%20daily%20newspaper%20Kristeligt%20Dagblad.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698132600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F7rrfp28o_israeli-hostages-released-daily-despatch_625x300_24_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdaily-despatch-hamas-frees-hostages-benjamin-netanyahus-ally-explains-ground-offensive-delay-4509165%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20Israeli%20hostages%2C%20held%20by%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20since%20October%207.%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20International%20Red%20Cross%20on%20Monday%20night.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdaily-despatch-hamas-frees-hostages-benjamin-netanyahus-ally-explains-ground-offensive-delay-4509165%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20filmed%20urinating%20in%20beer%20vat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698132120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-china-tsingtao_6333480.jpg%3F20231024093028%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftsingtao-chinese-brand-responds-after-man-filmed-urinating-in-beer-vats-12991430%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20was%20seen%20urinating%20into%20a%20vat%20at%20a%20Tsingtao%20beer%20factory%2C%20with%20the%20brand%20now%20opening%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20incident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%