's%20Office%20in%202011%2C%20and%20was%20later%20promoted%20as%20his%20Mr%20Patnaik's%20private%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandian's%20rise%20as%20the%20most%20trusted%20aide%20of%20the%20BJD%20chief%20has%20drawn%20fire%20from%20the%20the%20party's%20rivals%2C%20who%20have%20accused%20him%20of%20misusing%20a%20bureacrat's%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20his%20request%20for%20voluntary%20retirement%20came%20through%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Saptagiri%20Ulaka%20said%20he%20would%20not%20be%20surprised%20if%20Mr%20Pandian%20took%20charge%20as%20chief%20minister%20of%20Odisha%20before%20the%20next%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...such%20is%20the%20power%20structure%20in%20Odisha%2C%20no%20one%20has%20clue%20what's%20happening%20but%20everyone%20knows%20who's%20controlling.%20VRS%20approved%20in%203%20days%20during%20holidays%20-%20Super%20Fast%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20MLA%20SS%20Saluja%20said%20Mr%20Pandian%20should%20have%20quit%20public%20service%20earlier.%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20know%20whether%20he%20will%20join%20politics%20or%20return%20back%20to%20his%20own%20state.%20However%2C%20if%20he%20joins%20the%20BJD%2C%20then%20it%20will%20be%20helpful%20for%20the%20opposition%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20particular%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Saluja%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%20chief%20whip%20Mohan%20Majhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20he%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do%20politics%20openly%20instead%20of%20with%20the%20mask%20of%20a%20bureaucrat%20on.%20He%20will%20not%20be%20accepted%20by%20the%20people%20of%20Odisha.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698123840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fio4c0pqg_vk-pandian_625x300_24_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvk-pandian-gets-odisha-cabinet-minister-rank-after-voluntary-retirement-as-chief-minister-naveen-patnaiks-private-secretary-4508775%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20his%20request%20for%20a%20voluntary%20retirement%20came%20through%2C%20VK%20Pandian%2C%20former%20private%20secretary%20to%20Odisha%20Chief%20Minister%20Naveen%20Patnaik%2C%20has%20been%20given%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20rank%20in%20the%20state%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvk-pandian-gets-odisha-cabinet-minister-rank-after-voluntary-retirement-as-chief-minister-naveen-patnaiks-private-secretary-4508775%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvk-pandian-gets-odisha-cabinet-minister-rank-after-voluntary-retirement-as-chief-minister-naveen-patnaiks-private-secretary-4508775%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvk-pandian-gets-odisha-cabinet-minister-rank-after-voluntary-retirement-as-chief-minister-naveen-patnaiks-private-secretary-4508775%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Player%20Power%20Over%20Personal%20Success%3A%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi's%20True%20Impact%20on%20Indian%20Cricket%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24083208%2FF9JMon9WoAAF2wq.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOne%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20cricketers%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20(77)%20breathed%20his%20last%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%2023.%20This%20is%20an%20excerpt%20from%20Rajdeep%20Sardesai%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3EDemocracy%E2%80%99s%20XI%3A%20The%20Great%20Indian%20Cricket%20Story%3Cem%3E%2C%20published%20by%20Juggernaut%20in%202017.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%201966%2C%20when%20Bedi%20first%20represented%20India%2C%20to%20the%20tail%20end%20of%20his%20career%20in%20the%20late%201970s%2C%20India%20underwent%20a%20glorious%20spin%20revolution%20that%20would%20change%20Indian%20cricket%20forever.%20Brahma%2C%20the%20creator%20God%20in%20the%20Trimurti%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20has%20four%20faces%20looking%20in%20four%20different%20directions.%20But%20even%20he%20would%20have%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20recreate%20the%20magic%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20spin%20quartet%20which%20dominated%20the%20sport%20for%20a%20decade%20and%20more.%20And%20mirroring%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20unique%20notion%20of%20unity%20in%20diversity%2C%20the%20four%20Indian%20spinners%20were%20distinctive%20individuals%20with%20sharply%20contrasting%20personalities%20but%20united%20in%20their%20purpose%20of%20taking%20wickets%20for%20India.%20It%20was%20like%20having%20four%20magicians%20perform%20in%20one%20show%2C%20each%20with%20a%20unique%20bag%20of%20tricks%2C%20each%20luring%20an%20unsuspecting%20batsman%20to%20his%20doom%20with%20their%20mastery%20over%20flight%20and%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EErapalli%20Prasanna%2C%20who%20made%20his%20debut%20in%201962%2C%20was%20the%20oldest%20of%20the%20four.%20He%20was%20a%20true-blue%20Kannadiga%20born%20in%20Shimoga%2C%20another%20remote%20corner%20in%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20metro-centric%20geography%20at%20the%20time.%20As%20an%20off-spinner%2C%20he%20was%20almost%20a%20right-arm%20version%20of%20Bedi%2C%20shorter%20and%20stockier%20but%20with%20the%20same%20instinct%20to%20play%20mind%20games%20with%20batsmen%20through%20his%20control%20over%20the%20spinning%20ball.%20%E2%80%98We%20were%20like%20Siamese%20twins%20I%20guess%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20says%20with%20a%20chuckle.%20%E2%80%98We%20would%20share%20secrets%20and%20plot%20how%20to%20get%20a%20batsman%20out.%20It%20was%20almost%20as%20if%20we%20could%20read%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20minds.%E2%80%99%20Prasanna%20was%20a%20qualified%20engineer%2C%20even%20giving%20up%20the%20sport%20for%20five%20years%20after%20his%20first%20Test%20series%20because%20his%20father%20wanted%20him%20to%20complete%20his%20engineering%20degree%20first.%20%E2%80%98In%20those%20days%2C%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20studies%20first%2C%20then%20cricket.%20My%20father%2C%20who%20was%20a%20government%20servant%2C%20allowed%20me%20to%20go%20on%20my%20first%20cricket%20tour%20in%201962%20only%20because%20the%20Maharaja%20of%20Mysore%20intervened%20and%20promised%20him%20I%20would%20complete%20my%20degree%20on%20my%20return%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrasanna%E2%80%99s%20off-spinning%20rival%20was%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20Srinivas%20Venkataraghavan%2C%20another%20engineering%20graduate.%20Venkat%20fitted%20in%20with%20the%20stereotype%20of%20the%20stoic%2C%20unsmiling%20Tamil%20Brahmin%20and%20was%20a%20strict%20disciplinarian.%20I%20once%20met%20him%20at%20the%20Madras%20Cricket%20Club%20where%20he%20admonished%20a%20group%20of%20teenagers%20at%20the%20adjoining%20table%20for%20speaking%20too%20loudly.%20%E2%80%98He%20was%20the%20professor%2C%20the%20intellectual%20amongst%20us%20bon%20vivants.%20We%20would%20be%20having%20a%20drink%20and%20he%20would%20be%20reading%20a%20book%2C%E2%80%99%20says%20Bedi.%20Venkat%20was%20more%20than%20just%20a%20spinner%2C%20though%3B%20unlike%20the%20others%2C%20he%20was%20a%20decent%20batsman%20and%20a%20fine%20close-in%20fielder%20who%20would%20later%20even%20go%20on%20to%20become%20an%20international%20umpire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20maestro%20making%20up%20this%20incredible%20foursome%20was%20also%20the%20most%20enigmatic%20and%20fascinating.%20Bhagwat%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20another%20Kannadiga%2C%20was%20a%20truly%20heroic%20figure.%20An%20attack%20of%20polio%20at%20a%20very%20young%20age%20had%20withered%20his%20right%20arm%20but%20that%20did%20not%20stop%20him%20from%20becoming%2C%20arguably%2C%20the%20greatest%20match-winning%20bowler%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20history.%20He%20was%20unconventional%20in%20every%20sense%3B%20he%20would%20take%20a%20long%20run-up%20for%20a%20spinner%20and%20bowl%20leg-spinning%20deliveries%20with%20a%20pace%20and%20variety%20that%20foxed%20the%20best%20players.%20The%20sight%20of%20Chandrasekhar%20with%20the%20ball%2C%20marking%20his%20run-up%2C%20was%20enough%20for%20an%20entire%20stadium%20in%20Mumbai%20or%20Kolkata%20to%20shout%20in%20unison%2C%20%E2%80%98Boowwlled%E2%80%99.%20The%20sound%20would%20echo%20with%20a%20frenzy%20that%20would%20leave%20overseas%20batsmen%20shaken%20even%20before%20they%20played%20a%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Chandrasekhar%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20playing%20cricket%2C%20he%20liked%20to%20be%20far%20away%20from%20the%20action%2C%20quietly%20listening%20to%20a%20song%20by%20Mukesh%20or%20Saigal.%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20wanted%20to%20find%20Chandra%20before%20a%20Test%20match%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20he%20would%20be%20in%20Mukesh%E2%80%99s%20house%20for%20a%20private%20music%20concert%2C%E2%80%99%20recalls%20Bedi.%20Even%20now%2C%20Chandrasekhar%20prefers%20to%20be%20a%20recluse%2C%20refusing%20to%20carry%20a%20mobile%20%E2%80%93%20or%20at%20least%20choosing%20not%20to%20share%20the%20number!%20%E2%80%93%20and%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20his%20time%20with%20his%20son%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20ask%20Syed%20Kirmani%2C%20arguably%20the%20finest%20Indian%20wicketkeeper%20who%20played%20a%20fair%20bit%20with%20the%20four%20spinners%2C%20to%20compare%20them.%20%E2%80%98Champions%2C%20all%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%98Chandra%20was%20a%20genius%20and%20keeping%20to%20him%20was%20the%20biggest%20challenge.%20He%20could%20bowl%20leg-spin%2C%20googlies%20and%20top-spinners%20with%20almost%20the%20same%20action.%20And%20his%20faster%20one%20had%20the%20speed%20of%20a%20fast%20bowler.%20I%20remember%20he%20bowled%20a%20bouncer%20to%20Viv%20Richards%20once%20that%20went%20past%20the%20great%20batsman%E2%80%99s%20nose.%20Viv%20turned%20around%20and%20asked%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CIs%20this%20guy%20bowling%20spin%20or%20is%20he%20Jeff%20Thomson%20%5Bthe%20fastest%20bowler%20in%20the%20world%20in%20the%201970s%5D!%E2%80%9D%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20Bowled%20to%20Deceive%20but%2C%20Frank%20and%20Big-Hearted%2C%20Was%20the%20Least%20Deceptive%20of%20Men%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbishan-singh-bedi-bowled-to-deceive-but-frank-and-big-hearted-was-the-least-deceptive-of-men%5C%22%3EBishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20Bowled%20to%20Deceive%20but%2C%20Frank%20and%20Big-Hearted%2C%20Was%20the%20Least%20Deceptive%20of%20Men%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EContinues%20Kirmani%2C%20%E2%80%98Prasanna%20was%20a%20wily%20fox%20who%20would%20defeat%20you%20in%20the%20air.%20His%20loop%20was%20such%20as%20if%20he%20was%20holding%20the%20ball%20on%20a%20string%20like%20a%20puppet-master.%20Venkat%20was%20not%20in%20the%20same%20league%2C%20he%20was%20flatter%20with%20his%20deliveries%20but%20very%20exact%20and%20determined.%20And%20Bedi%20was%20simply%20poetry%20in%20action.%20He%20could%20bowl%20six%20different%20deliveries%20in%20an%20over%2C%20including%20an%20armer%2C%20with%20the%20most%20effortless%20style.%20When%20you%20watched%20him%20bowl%2C%20you%20felt%20as%20if%20you%20were%20in%20a%20museum%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20great%20artist.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20342px)%2085vw%2C%20342px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24103037%2F71-KeS04QIL._SL1400_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22342%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24103037%2F71-KeS04QIL._SL1400_.jpg%20777w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24103037%2F71-KeS04QIL._SL1400_-194x300.jpg%20194w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24103037%2F71-KeS04QIL._SL1400_-663x1024.jpg%20663w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681489%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22528%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERajdeep%20Sardesai%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EDemocracy%E2%80%99s%20XI%3A%20The%20Great%20Indian%20Cricket%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EJuggernaut%2C%202017%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhy%20did%20India%20become%20the%20land%20of%20spinners%20while%20neighbouring%20Pakistan%20produced%20fast%20bowlers%3F%20The%20conventional%20explanation%20is%20the%20differing%20physical%20attributes%20of%20the%20two%20South%20Asian%20neighbours.%20The%20tall%20and%20muscular%20Pakistanis%20were%20seen%20to%20possess%20the%20physique%20to%20bowl%20fast%20while%20the%20less%20well-built%20Indians%20were%20more%20adept%20at%20bowling%20spin.%20I%20offer%20a%20slight%20variation%20to%20the%20theory.%20In%20India%2C%20cricket%20was%20an%20elite%20and%20urban%20middle-class%20sport%20till%20Kapil%20Dev%E2%80%99s%20team%20won%20the%201983%20World%20Cup%20and%20opened%20up%20the%20sport%20to%20a%20new%20generation.%20The%20Indian%20team%20was%20mostly%20full%20of%20players%20belonging%20to%20the%20Brahminical%20upper%20castes%20who%20perhaps%20considered%20fast%20bowling%20hard%20labour%2C%20especially%20in%20hot%20weather%20with%20unforgiving%20pitches.%20It%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20three%20of%20the%20four%20spinning%20greats%20were%20urban%20Brahmins%20and%20mostly%20vegetarian%20with%20the%20Jat%20Sikh%20Bedi%20the%20only%20exception.%20The%20image%20of%20the%20Brahmin%20as%20more%20learned%20and%20less%20physical%20fits%20in%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20spin%20bowling%20as%20an%20art%20form%20where%20mind%20scores%20over%20muscle.%20When%20I%20suggest%20this%20to%20Prasanna%2C%20he%20laughs.%20%E2%80%98We%20were%20vegetarian%20in%20our%20food%20habits%2C%20but%20strictly%20non-vegetarian%20when%20we%20were%20gobbling%20up%20opposing%20batsmen!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBetween%20them%2C%20the%20spin%20quartet%20picked%20up%20an%20astonishing%20853%20Test%20wickets.%20By%20contrast%2C%20the%20great%20West%20Indian%20fast%20bowling%20equivalent%20of%20Andy%20Roberts%2C%20Joel%20Garner%2C%20Michael%20Holding%20and%20Colin%20Croft%20put%20together%20had%20835%20wickets.%20Of%20the%2098%20Test%20matches%20in%20which%20one%20or%20more%20of%20the%20spinners%20played%20together%2C%20India%20won%2023%2C%20lost%2036%20and%20drew%2039%20games.%20If%20those%20aren%E2%80%99t%20striking%20figures%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20put%20them%20in%20context%20%E2%80%93%20India%20won%20only%207%20out%20of%2076%20Tests%20till%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20spinners.%20%E2%80%98I%20think%20they%20changed%20the%20way%20we%20played%20the%20game.%20Until%20the%20spinners%20came%2C%20our%20main%20aim%20was%20not%20to%20lose%20the%20match.%20Now%20we%20could%20think%20of%20actually%20trying%20to%20win%20games%2C%E2%80%99%20explains%20former%20India%20captain%20Ajit%20Wadekar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWadekar%20should%20know.%20He%20was%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20team%20that%20scored%20a%20hat-trick%20of%20victories%20over%20the%20West%20Indies%20and%20England%20between%201970%20and%201973%2C%20wins%20that%20catapulted%20Indian%20cricket%20on%20to%20the%20world%20stage.%20The%20finest%20performance%20was%20probably%20at%20the%20Oval%20in%20London%20in%201971%20when%20India%20defeated%20England%20on%20its%20home%20turf%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20This%20is%20how%20my%20late%20father%20Dilip%20Sardesai%20remembers%20the%20game.%20%E2%80%98The%20wicket%20was%20turning%20when%20Wadekar%20brought%20Chandra%20on%20to%20bowl.%20Chandra%20and%20I%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20horse%20races%20on%20the%20rest%20day%20of%20the%20match.%20A%20horse%20called%20Mildred%20won%20a%20race.%20When%20John%20Edrich%20came%20to%20bat%2C%20I%20told%20Chandra%3A%20%E2%80%9CIsko%20Mildred%20daal%20%5Bbowl%20him%20a%20Mildred%5D.%E2%80%9D%20He%20bowled%20the%20most%20vicious%20googly%20and%20shattered%20the%20stumps.%20After%20that%2C%20Chandra%20was%20unplayable%20and%20the%20English%20batsmen%20were%20psychologically%20destroyed.%20When%20we%20won%20the%20game%20the%20next%20day%2C%20it%20seemed%20as%20if%20every%20Indian%20living%20in%20England%20was%20at%20the%20Oval.%20One%20of%20them%20offered%20us%20free%20food%20and%20drink%20for%20life%20in%20his%20restaurant%20and%20named%20dishes%20after%20us!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20that%20August%20day%20at%20the%20Oval%20in%201971%2C%20Indian%20cricket%20had%20tasted%20real%20freedom.%20Just%20months%20later%2C%20India%20would%20go%20to%20war%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20liberate%20Bangladesh%20in%20a%20decisive%20military%20triumph%20that%20renewed%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20self-confidence%2C%20earlier%20dented%20by%20the%20defeat%20in%20the%201962%20Sino-Indian%20war.%20Chandrasekhar%20picked%20up%206%20wickets%2C%20Venkat%202%20and%20Bedi%201.%20The%20mantra%20of%20non-violence%20as%20defined%20by%20spin%20had%20won%20the%20day%20for%20the%20Indians%20yet%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20match-winning%20performances%20would%20continue%20for%20at%20least%20another%20seven%20years%20till%20the%20fingers%20and%20arms%20began%20to%20tire.%20The%20great%20Indian%20spin%20quartet%20was%20conquered%20on%20the%20first%20tour%20to%20Pakistan%20in%201978.%20The%20host%20team%E2%80%99s%20batting%2C%20led%20by%20Zaheer%20Abbas%20and%20Javed%20Miandad%2C%20was%20in%20prime%20form%20on%20flat%20batting%20tracks%20and%20the%20ageing%20Indian%20bowling%20attack%20just%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20match%20up.%20The%20spinners%20would%20be%20quickly%20pushed%20into%20retirement.%20%E2%80%98It%20happened%20a%20little%20suddenly%20and%20was%20unfortunate%20but%20we%20had%20a%20bloody%20good%20ride%20along%20the%20way%2C%E2%80%99%20Prasanna%20reflects%20on%20the%20endgame.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEngland%20would%20be%20the%20venue%20of%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20final%20series%20in%201979.%20He%20was%20only%20thirty-three%20when%20he%20played%20his%20last%20Test%2C%20a%20relatively%20young%20age%20for%20a%20spinner.%20But%20no%20one%20had%20bowled%20more%20overs%20through%20the%201970s%20than%20the%20sardar%20from%20Amritsar.%20No%20one%20had%20taken%20more%20wickets%20for%20India%20when%20he%20retired%3A%20266%20wickets%20in%2067%20Tests.%20Only%20two%20left-arm%20spinners%2C%20Derek%20Underwood%20of%20England%20and%20Daniel%20Vettori%20of%20New%20Zealand%2C%20have%20taken%20more%20Test%20wickets.%20But%20no%20one%20has%20brought%20more%20joy%20to%20the%20cricket%20purist%3B%20when%20Bedi%20came%20in%20to%20bowl%20in%20his%20resplendent%20blue%20or%20pink%20patka%2C%20you%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20be%20transfixed%20by%20his%20action%2C%20smooth%20and%20rich%20as%20the%20milk%20in%20his%20hometown.%20The%20English%20off-spinner%20Jim%20Laker%20once%20said%20that%20his%20idea%20of%20heaven%20was%20%E2%80%98sunshine%20at%20Lord%E2%80%99s%2C%20Ray%20Lindwall%2C%20the%20Australian%20fast%20bowler%2C%20bowling%20from%20one%20end%2C%20Bedi%20from%20the%20other%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20critics%20say%20Bedi%20bowled%20like%20a%20millionaire%2C%20often%20giving%20away%20too%20many%20runs%20in%20his%20search%20for%20wickets.%20This%20is%20statistically%20untrue%3B%20Bedi%20is%20second%20best%20to%20the%20West%20Indian%20Lance%20Gibbs%20in%20terms%20of%20bowling%20maiden%20overs%20per%20Test%20match.%20Bedi%20explains%20his%20approach%20of%20clapping%20after%20being%20hit%20for%20six.%20%E2%80%98You%20bowl%20to%20get%20a%20batsman%20out.%20If%20a%20Test%20batsman%20hits%20a%20few%20fours%20or%20sixes%20but%20I%20get%20him%20out%20for%2030%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20better%20than%20bowling%20defensively%20and%20allowing%20him%20to%20just%20bat%20on%20and%20on%20and%20score%20a%20hundred%3F%E2%80%99%20The%20attacking%20instinct%20played%20a%20bit%20part%20in%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20prominent%20role%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20first-ever%20overseas%20wins%20in%20Australia%2C%20West%20Indies%2C%20England%20and%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESir%20Don%20Bradman%20suggests%20that%20Bedi%20is%20among%20the%20greatest%20left-%20arm%20spinners%20of%20all%20time.%20In%20a%20fitting%20tribute%2C%20Bradman%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%98Bedi%20was%20a%20real%20study%20for%20the%20connoisseur.%20His%20ideal%20well-balanced%20run-up%20always%20brought%20him%20into%20the%20perfect%20delivery%20position.%20The%20ball%20was%20held%20well%20in%20the%20tips%20of%20long%2C%20almost%20delicate%20fingers%20which%20never%20seemed%20to%20get%20tired%2C%20but%20always%20retained%20great%20flexibility%20and%20control.%20There%20were%20regular%20but%20very%20subtle%20changes%20of%20pace%20%E2%80%93%20variations%20in%20flight%2C%20and%20always%20coupled%20with%20genuine%20spin.%20The%20end%20product%20was%20a%20delight%20to%20watch%20and%20I%20do%20not%20hesitate%20to%20rank%20Bedi%20among%20the%20finest%20bowlers%20of%20his%20type%20we%20have%20seen.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20Indian%20cricketer%20had%20received%20higher%20praise%20from%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20ultimate%20icon.%20But%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20true%20impact%20on%20Indian%20cricket%20lies%20not%20just%20in%20his%20contribution%20to%20the%20art%20of%20left-arm%20spin%20bowling%20but%20in%20the%20way%20he%20redefined%20the%20idea%20of%20leadership%20in%20Indian%20sport%20by%20putting%20player%20power%20above%20personal%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698123729000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24083208%2FF9JMon9WoAAF2wq.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fplayer-power-over-personal-success-bishan-singh-bedis-true-impact-on-indian-cricket%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bedi%E2%80%99s%20true%20impact%20on%20Indian%20cricket%20lies%20not%20just%20in%20his%20contribution%20to%20the%20art%20of%20left-arm%20spin%20bowling%20but%20in%20the%20way%20he%20redefined%20the%20idea%20of%20leadership%20in%20Indian%20sport%20by%20putting%20player%20power%20above%20personal%20success.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fplayer-power-over-personal-success-bishan-singh-bedis-true-impact-on-indian-cricket%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suhana-Agastya%20spotted%20at%20Vikram%20Phadnis'%20b'day%22%2