%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Stand%20By%20What%20I%20Said%26quot%3B%3A%20Chief%20Justice%20On%20Marriage%20Equality%20Judgment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChief%20Justices%20have%20been%20in%20the%20minority%20in%2013%20significant%20judgments%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20has%20said%2C%20standing%20by%20his%20recent%20ruling%20in%20the%20marriage%20equality%20case.%C2%A0He%20was%20speaking%20yesterday%20at%20the%203rd%20Comparative%20Constitutional%20Law%20discussion%20on%20'Perspectives%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Courts%20of%20India%20and%20the%20United%20States'%2C%20hosted%20by%20Georgetown%20University%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20believe%20it%20is%20sometimes%20a%20vote%20of%20conscience%20and%20a%20vote%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20And%20I%20stand%20by%20what%20I%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20October%2017%20judgment%20in%20which%20it%20stopped%20short%20of%20legalising%20same-sex%20marriages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20judges%20on%20the%20five-member%20Constitution%20bench%20agreed%20that%20tweaking%20laws%20to%20bring%20about%20marriage%20equality%20would%20amount%20to%20encroaching%20into%20the%20legislature's%20domain.%20There%20was%2C%20however%2C%20a%20difference%20of%20opinion%20on%20the%20question%20of%20the%20right%20to%20civil%20union%20and%20adoption%20rights.%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20and%20Justice%20SK%20Kaul%20were%20in%20favour%20of%20recognising%20same-sex%20unions.%20The%20majority%20of%20the%20bench%20took%20a%20different%20view%2C%20with%20Justice%20S%20Ravindra%20Bhat%20saying%20he%20disagreed%20with%20the%20court%20directing%20the%20State%20to%20provide%20for%20a%20new%20legal%20framework%20to%20formalise%20such%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20also%20stood%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20judgment%20of%20leaving%20the%20decision%20on%20marriage%20equality%20to%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20the%20unanimous%20verdict%20of%20all%20the%20five%20judges%20on%20the%20bench%2C%20we%20came%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20while%20we%20have%20progressed%20a%20great%20deal%20in%20terms%20of%20decriminalising%20homosexuality%20and%20recognising%20people%20belonging%20to%20the%20queer%20community%20as%20equal%20participants%20in%20our%20society%2C%20legislating%20on%20the%20right%20to%20marry%20is%20something%20that%20falls%20within%20the%20domain%20of%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20judgment%20in%20the%20closely-watched%20case%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20had%20said%20choosing%20a%20life%20partner%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20choosing%20one's%20course%20of%20life.%20%26quot%3BSome%20may%20regard%20this%20as%20the%20most%20important%20decision%20of%20their%20life.%20This%20right%20goes%20to%20the%20root%20of%20the%20right%20to%20life%20and%20liberty%20under%20Article%2021%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20right%20to%20enter%20into%20union%20includes%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20one's%20partner%20and%20the%20right%20to%20recognition%20of%20that%20union.%20A%20failure%20to%20recognise%20such%20associations%20will%20result%20in%20discrimination%20against%20queer%20couples%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20right%20to%20enter%20into%20union%20cannot%20be%20restricted%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20sexual%20orientation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESupporting%20adoption%20rights%20for%20queer%20couples%2C%20he%20said%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20probe%20that%20only%20heterosexual%20couples%20can%20provide%20stability%20to%20a%20child.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20material%20on%20record%20to%20prove%20that%20only%20a%20married%20heterosexual%20couple%20can%20provide%20stability%20to%20a%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698123600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F20