NDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fnagpur%2Fram-temple-at-ayodhya-to-open-from-january-22-rss-chief-mohan-bhagwat%2Farticleshow%2F104666312.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ten%20Years%20After%20SC%E2%80%99s%20Landmark%20Judgment%2C%20Dongria%20Kondhs%20in%20Niyamgiri%20Still%20Suffer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101346%2FNH1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20decade%20since%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fpdf%2FSupremeCourtReport%2F2013_v6_piv.pdf%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20landmark%20judgement%20in%202013%3C%2Fa%3E%20upholding%20the%20rights%20of%20%3Cem%3Egram%20sabhas%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20Niyamgiri%2C%20Rayagada%2C%20and%20Kalahandi%20(Odisha)%20against%20the%20conversion%20of%20forest%20land%20for%20proposed%20bauxite%20mining%20by%20Vedanta%20Alumina%20company.%20The%20judgment%20was%20a%20watershed%20moment%20for%20the%20decentralisation%20of%20power%2C%20grassroots%20democracy%2C%20and%20tribal%20rights%20over%20forest%20and%20land%20under%20the%20fifth%20scheduled%20areas%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20halted%20the%20advancement%20of%20bauxite%20mining%20on%20the%20top%20of%20Niyamgiri%20Hill%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20(a%20Particularly%20Vulnerable%20Tribal%20Group)%20continues%20to%20live%20there.%20However%2C%20despite%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20judgment%20protecting%20the%20community%20rights%20of%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20over%20Niyamgiri%2C%20their%20difficulties%20have%20continued.%20Government%20facilities%20are%20still%20a%20distant%20dream%2C%20and%20they%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20mental%20and%20emotional%20pressure%20of%20uncertainty%20and%20police%20surveillance%2C%20and%20violence%20in%20their%20day-to-day%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPublic%20infrastructure%20is%20still%20a%20distant%20dream%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20research%20team%2C%20we%20visited%20the%20Lakhpadar%20village%20situated%20on%20the%20top%20of%20Niyamgiri%20Hill.%20We%20travelled%20around%2010-15%20km%20from%20Lanjigarh%20to%20reach%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20village%20Phuldumer%2C%20which%20has%20a%20proper%20road%20and%20is%20situated%20on%20the%20base%20of%20Niygamgiri%20Hill.%20After%20that%2C%20we%20travelled%20another%20four%20kilometers%20on%20a%20steep%20metal%20road%20to%20reach%20a%20village%20called%20Tadijhola.%20From%20there%2C%20we%20climbed%20the%20forest%20and%20walked%20for%20one%20hour%20to%20reach%20another%20village%20called%20Lakhpadar.%20In%20between%2C%20we%20crossed%20as%20many%20as%20ten%20springs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESurrounded%20by%20a%20dense%20forest%2C%20the%20100%20metres%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20village%20has%20a%20newly%20constructed%20concrete%20road.%20There%20are%20around%2025%20houses%20constructed%20in%20two%20rows%2C%20with%20all%20houses%20covered%20with%20tin%20rooftops.%20The%20main%20street%20of%20the%20village%20is%20rough%2C%20with%20rock%20layers%2C%20and%20is%20steep%20on%20one%20side.%20The%20villagers%20depend%20on%20spring%20water%20connected%20through%20pipes%20and%20taps%3B%20the%20spring%20water%20is%20also%20used%20for%20bathing%20and%20other%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%202011%20census%2C%20the%20village%20has%20a%20population%20of%20270%20(115%20men%20and%20155%20women).%20It%20has%2059%20households%2C%20and%20the%20literacy%20rate%20is%200.47%25.%20There%20is%20no%20school%20or%20anganwadi%20centre%20in%20the%20village.%20They%20mostly%20depend%20upon%20traditional%20healthcare%20methods%2C%20and%20no%20healthcare%20center%20is%20nearby.%20The%20panchayat%20office%20Parsali%2C%20under%20Kalyangsingpur%20Bolk%2C%20district%20Rayagada%2C%20is%20around%2010%20km%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPhuldumer%2C%20Kunakadu%2C%20Tadijhola%2C%20and%20Lakhpadar%20are%20among%20the%2012%20villages%20where%20a%20gram%20sabha%20meeting%20was%20conducted%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order.%20The%20Dongria%20Kondh%20of%20the%20Niyamgiri%20Hills%20live%20in%20four%20community%20blocks%20%E2%80%93%20Muniguda%2C%20Raygada%2C%20and%20Kalyansingpur%20in%20Rayagada%20and%20Lanjigarh%20block%20in%20Kalahandi%20district.%20The%20majority%20of%20them%20live%20in%20the%20Rayagada%20district%2C%20as%20most%20of%20the%20Niyamgiri%20Hills%20come%20under%20the%20Rayagada%20district.%20These%20villages%20have%20very%20limited%20public%20infrastructure%20facilities%20like%20schools%2C%20healthcare%20centers%2C%20roads%2C%20transport%20services%2C%20markets%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20baseline%20survey%20by%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Research%20and%20Training%20Institute%20(2016)%20Odisha%20reveals%20that%20the%20total%20Dongria%20Kondh%20population%20in%20Rayagada%20district%20is%207%2C722%20(4%2C443%20women%20and%203%2C279%20men)%20living%20in%201%2C892%20families.%20They%20live%20in%2098%20villages%20with%20extremely%20minimal%20infrastructure%20facilities.%20For%20instance%2C%20only%2031%20of%20these%20villages%20have%20schools%2C%20while%2028%20villages%20have%20anganwadi%20centres.%20Only%2016%20villages%20are%20connected%20with%20motorable%20roads.%20The%20literacy%20rate%20among%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20is%2029%25%2C%20out%20of%20which%20the%20male%20literacy%20rate%20is%2024.5%25%20and%20the%20female%20literacy%20rate%20is%2015.9%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101559%2FNH3.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22696%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101559%2FNH3.png%20696w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101559%2FNH3-300x186.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681485%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22432%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDemography%2C%20literacy%20and%20available%20basic%20infrastructure%20for%20Dongria%20Kondh%20in%20Niyamgiri%2C%20Rayagada.%20Source%3A%20SCs%20%26amp%3B%20STs%20Research%20Institute%20(SCSTRTI)%2C%20Government%20of%20Odisha%20(2016).%20Conservation-%20cum-%20Development%20Plan%20for%20Dangaria%20Kandha%20PVTG.%20DKDA%2C%20Kurli%2C%20Chatikona%2C%20Rayagada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20uncertain%20future%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Dongria%20Kondh%20depend%20upon%20shifting%20cultivation%20and%20collection%20of%20minor%20forest%20products%20for%20their%20livelihood.%20They%20have%20still%20maintained%20their%20unique%20way%20of%20life%2C%20maintaining%20their%20social%2C%20religious%20and%20cultural%20practices%20and%20beliefs%20which%20are%20different%20from%20the%20caste%20society.%20An%20activist%20who%20shares%20a%20close%20bond%20with%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cearlier%2C%20they%20were%20not%20participating%20in%20elections%20and%20were%20unaware%20of%20the%20police%20and%20judiciary%20system%2C%20as%20this%20system%20had%20not%20reached%20them.%20There%20was%20no%20road%20and%20connectivity%2C%20no%20school%20and%20anganwadi%20even%20today.%20However%2C%20after%20Vedanta%20came%20to%20Niyamgiri%20they%20protested%20and%20came%20into%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20police%2C%20judiciary%20and%20outside%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELada%20Sikaka%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20and%20president%20of%20Niyamgiri%20Suraksha%20Samiti%2C%20recalled%20their%20protest%20against%20the%20mining%20and%20life%20thereafter%20with%20pain.%20He%20said%20that%20till%20now%2C%20they%20have%20not%20allowed%20Vedanta%20to%20mine%20on%20their%20sacred%20land%2C%20and%20he%20is%20hopeful%20that%20the%20next%20generation%20will%20continue%20to%20save%20their%20land.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20living%20in%20this%20forest%20for%20generations.%20This%20is%20our%20%3Cem%3Emata%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mother)%20that%20gives%20us%20food%2C%20a%20living%2C%20and%20water.%20If%20the%20company%20displaces%20us%2C%20we%20will%20die.%20If%20our%20%3Cem%3Emata%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20erased%2C%20then%20how%20can%20we%20live%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20company%20came%20to%20the%20area%2C%20their%20struggles%20have%20doubled%2C%20Sikaka%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20fought%20and%20we%20won.%20The%20company%20had%20come%20and%20started%20some%20work%20near%20our%20sacred%20place%20where%20we%20worship%20Niyam%20Raja%20Niyam%20God)%20and%20we%20had%20no%20other%20choice%20than%20to%20oppose%20it%20strongly%2C%E2%80%9D%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20is%20still%20worried%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20company%20taking%20over%20their%20sacred%20hill.%20Organising%20against%20the%20Vedanta%20project%2C%20and%20the%20turmoil%20and%20uncertainty%20that%20brought%2C%20meant%20they%20had%20to%20take%20time%20away%20from%20their%20daily%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101501%2FNH2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101501%2FNH2.png%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101501%2FNH2-300x186.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681484%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20Dongria%20Kondh%20village%20in%20Niyamgiri%20Hill.%20Photo%3A%20Author%20provided%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContinuous%20police%20surveillance%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2029%2C%20there%20was%20news%20in%20the%20evening%20that%20environmental%20activist%20Prafulla%20Samantara%20had%20been%20kidnapped%20from%20a%20private%20lodge%20in%20the%20district%20headquarter%20Rayagada%20and%20was%20released%C2%A0%20in%20Berhamapur%2C%20which%20is%20205%20km%20away.%20He%20had%20come%20to%20meet%20the%20arrested%20leaders%20of%20the%20Niyamgiri%20Surakha%20Samiti%20and%20was%20supposed%20to%20address%20a%20press%20conference%20after%20that.%20He%20alleged%20that%20his%20unlawful%20detention%20was%20done%20either%20by%20the%20police%20or%20goons%20hired%20by%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20August%209%2C%20when%20the%20whole%20world%20was%20celebrating%20World%20Indigenous%20Day%2C%20the%20Dongria%20Kondhs%20of%20Niyamgiri%20Hill%20and%20their%20supporters%20were%20arrested%20and%20slapped%20with%20the%20UAPA%20by%20the%20Odisha%20police%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20attending%20a%20celebration%20and%20protest%20gathering.%20Those%20who%20were%20charged%20include%20Lada%20Sikaka%2C%20Drenju%20Krushka%2C%20Manu%20Sikaka%20and%20Saamba%20Huika%20(all%20from%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20community)%20and%20their%20supporters%20like%20Lingaraj%20Azad%2C%20Upendra%20Bag%20and%20Lenin%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELingaraj%20Azad%2C%20an%20activist%20and%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Niyamgiri%20Suraksha%20Samiti%2C%20said%20that%20just%20before%20World%20Indigenous%20Day%2C%20two%20Dongria%20Kondh%20young%20men%20were%20picked%20up%20while%20they%20were%20on%20their%20way%20home%20from%20shopping.%20After%20four%20or%20five%20days%20of%20protest%2C%20villagers%20came%20to%20know%20that%20they%20had%20been%20detained%20by%20the%20police%2C%20who%20initially%20denied%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%20matter.%20Finally%2C%20they%20released%20one%20youth%2C%20while%20the%20other%20was%20charged%20in%20a%20rape%20case.%20Surprisingly%2C%20neither%20he%20nor%20anyone%20else%20knows%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20and%20the%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20in%20the%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELingaraj%20Azad%20alleged%20that%20police%20framed%20innocent%20Dongria%20Kondhs%20and%20their%20supporters%20under%20false%20charges%2C%20and%20used%20the%20draconian%20UAPA%20to%20try%20and%20silence%20them.%20He%20counts%C2%A0%20more%20than%2020%20who%20have%20been%20falsely%20framed%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Lada%20Sikaka%2C%20police%20surveillance%20and%20violence%20began%20only%20after%20Vedanta%20came%20to%20Lanjigarh%20and%20proposed%20to%20mine%20on%20their%20land.%20He%20has%20been%20arrested%20thrice%20by%20the%20police%20under%20various%20charges%20that%20he%20does%20not%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWay%20forward%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELooking%20into%20the%20socio-economic%20situation%20of%20Dongria%20Kondhs%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20basic%20public%20infrastructure%20in%20Niyamgiri%2C%20and%20the%20police%20violence%2C%20the%20question%20that%20comes%20to%20mind%20is%2C%20how%20sensitive%20is%20the%20state%20police%20while%20dealing%20with%20a%20Particularly%20Vulnerable%20Tribal%20Group%20like%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%3F%20More%20than%20the%20police%2C%20what%20they%20needed%20was%20a%20teacher%2C%20an%20anganwadi%20and%20road%20and%20transportation%20infrastructure.%20The%20police%20cannot%20bring%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr%20Deepak%20Kumar%20Nanda%20is%20a%20development%20researcher%20and%20currently%20teaches%20at%20the%20Central%20University%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20Ranchi.%20Dr%20Bipon%20Jojo%20is%20a%20professor%20at%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20Mumbai.%20Views%20expressed%20above%20are%20personal.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698123119000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101346%2FNH1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ften-years-after-scs-landmark-judgment-dongria-kondhs-in-niyamgiri-still-suffer%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Public%20infrastructure%20is%20yet%20to%20reach%20the%20area%20and%20benefit%20this%20Particularly%20Vulnerable%20Tribal%20Group.%20But%20the%20police%20state%20is%20all%20too%20visible%2C%20filing%20allegedly%20false%20cases%20against%20the%20community%20and%20those%20who%20raise%20their%20voice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ften-years-after-scs-landmark-judgment-dongria-kondhs-in-niyamgiri-still-suffer%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDon't%20See%20Any%20Attitude%20From%20Team...%26quot%3B%3A%20Babar%20Tears%20Into%20Pakistan%20Players%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20brink%20of%20elimination%20from%20the%20World%20Cup%20after%20their%20shock%20defeat%20to%20Afghanistan%2C%20Pakistan%20captain%20Babar%20Azam%20said%20his%20players%20showed%20lack%20of%20attitude%20while%20fielding%20and%20they%20need%20extra%20effort%20in%20that%20department%20of%20the%20game.%20The%20eight-wicket%20loss%20on%20Monday%20was%20Pakistan's%20third%20defeat%20on%20the%20trot%20after%20starting%20the%20tournament%20with%20back-to-back%20wins.%20The%20stunning%20defeat%20literally%20pushed%20Pakistan%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20elimination%20as%20they%20will%20need%20to%20win%20all%20their%20remaining%20four%20matches%20to%20be%20sure%20of%20a%20semifinal%20berth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgainst%20Afghanistan%2C%20Babar's%20men%20were%20sloppy%20in%20fielding%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20boundary%20and%20in%20conceding%20a%20couple%20of%20overthrows.%20He%20blamed%20it%20on%20the%20lack%20of%20attitude%20from%20his%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20you%20do%20fielding%2C%20it%20is%20only%20with%20attitude.%20And%20I%20don't%20see%20any%20attitude%20from%20the%20team.%20You%20need%20to%20put%20in%20extra%20effort%20and%20be%20fit%2C%26quot%3B%20Babar%20said%20at%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20should%20focus%20on%20the%20ball%2C%20not%20on%20other%20thoughts%2C%20and%20when%20the%20ball%20comes%2C%20as%20a%20fielder%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20proactive.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20we%20are%20lagging%20a%20little%20bit%20as%20a%20fielding%20unit.%26quot%3B%20Pakistan%20play%20South%20Africa%20here%20on%20Friday%20and%20that%20will%20be%20a%20make-or-break%20match%20for%20them.%20Babar%20said%20his%20team%20needs%20a%20new%20approach%20in%20the%20remaining%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20have%20to%20go%20with%20a%20different%20plan%2C%20a%20different%20mindset%2C%20we%20will%20try%20to%20bring%20a%20positive%20vibe%20in%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20we%20learn%20from%20this%20loss%20(against%20Afghanistan).%20It%20will%20hurt%20us%20a%20lot.%20We%20will%20try%20to%20talk%20about%20positive%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20we%20will%20also%20talk%20about%20the%20things%20we%20did%20not%20do%20well.%20How%20we%20will%20do%20it%20in%20the%20future.%20Because%20every%20match%20is%20with%20a%20different%20team.%26quot%3B%20Babar%20admitted%20that%20his%20team%20has%20been%20sloppy%20in%20one%20department%20of%20the%20game%20or%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%2C%20we%20do%20well%20in%20bowling%2C%20(but)%20we%20don't%20do%20well%20in%20batting.%20When%20we%20do%20well%20in%20batting%2C%20we%20don't%20do%20it%20in%20fielding.%26quot%3B%20Pakistan%20pace%20bowling%20attack%20is%20rated%20as%20one%20of%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%20but%20it%20has%20failed%20to%20live%20up%20to%20the%20expectations%20in%20this%20tournament%2C%20leaking%20runs%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBabar%20admitted%20that%20the%20absence%20of%20pacer%20Naseem%20Shah%20has%20hurt%20the%20team%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20missing%20Naseem%20a%20lot.%20But%20apart%20from%20that%2C%20our%20bowling%20lineup%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best.%20But%2C%20I%20think%20we%20are%20not%20able%20to%20click.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20lose%20for%20the%20side%20and%20they%20will%20give%20their%20best%20in%20the%20remaining%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20team%20was%20facing%20a%20dip%20in%20confidence%20after%20losing%20to%20arch-rivals%20Indian%20in%20their%20third%20match%2C%20Azam%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20so.%20It's%20not%20like%20that.%20We%20have%20seen%20in%20Australia's%20match%2C%20we%20had%20scored%20almost%20three%20hundred.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20bowling%2C%20we%20started%20badly%2C%20but%20we%20finished%20up%20well.%20But%20I%20don't%20think%20we%20have%20anything%20to%20lose.%20Every%20team%20is%20a%20new%20match%2C%20and%20we%20try%20to%20give%20our%20best.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698122760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fbmevcp_babar-azam-icc_625x300_24_October_23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fdont-see-any-attitude-from-team-while-babar-azam-tears-into-pakistan-players-4508796%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Against%20Afghanistan%2C%20Babar's%20men%20were%20sloppy%20in%20fielding%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20boundary%20and%20in%20conceding%20a%20couple%20of%20overthrows.%20He%20blamed%20it%20on%20the%20lack%20of%20attitude%20from%20his%20players.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A228%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fdont-see-any-attitude-from-te