0by%20himself%2C%20and%20I%20take%20the%20stage%20separately%20by%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20party%20(the%20Mizo%20National%20Front)%20had%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20said%2C%20because%20they%20were%20against%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20policy%20to%20provide%20shelter%20to%20refugees%20from%20Manipur%2C%20Myanmar%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20Zoramthanga%20said%20his%20government%20was%20following%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20government%20helped%20the%20refugees%20from%20the%20erstwhile%20East%20Pakistan%20and%20even%20armed%20them%20to%20attain%20independence.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20arm%20the%20refugees%20from%20Myanmar%20but%20we%20simply%20provide%20them%20food%20and%20shelter%20on%20humanitarian%20grounds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmizroam-to-ignore-centres-order-to-collect-biometric-data-of-refugees-from-myanmar%5C%22%3EZoramthanga%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20government%20would%20not%20be%20following%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20directive%20to%20collect%20biometric%20data%20from%20refugees.%20%E2%80%9CCollection%20of%20biometric%20and%20biographic%20data%20of%20Myanmar%20refugees%20would%20amount%20to%20discrimination%20against%20people%20who%20are%20of%20our%20blood%20and%20kindred%20brothers%20and%20sisters.%20Keeping%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20not%20to%20undertake%20this%20as%20of%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fzoramthanga-on-ucc-and-manipur-violence%5C%22%3Espoken%20out%20against%3C%2Fa%3E%20plans%20for%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20which%20several%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20been%20pushing.%20He%20has%20also%20raised%20his%20voice%20on%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20several%20times%2C%20which