umorously%20remarked%2C%20%26quot%3B'Crooked%20Joe%20can't%20even%20walk%20up%20the%20children's%20stairs%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trump-ridicules-joe-biden-for-using-childrens-stairs-on-air-force-one%2Farticleshow%2F104665044.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trump-ridicules-joe-biden-for-using-childrens-stairs-on-air-force-one%2Famp_articleshow%2F104665044.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trump-ridicules-joe-biden-for-using-childrens-stairs-on-air-force-one%2Famp_articleshow%2F104665044.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20Military%20Vows%20%26quot%3BFull%20Dismantling%26quot%3B%20Of%20Hamas%20Amid%20Ongoing%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20it%20was%20preparing%20for%20%26quot%3Bunrelenting%20attacks%26quot%3B%20to%20dismantle%20Hamas%20while%20former%20U.S.%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20warned%20that%20%26quot%3Bany%20Israeli%20military%20strategy%20that%20ignores%20the%20human%20costs%20could%20ultimately%20backfire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20health%20ministry%20said%20the%20Gaza%20death%20toll%20in%20two%20weeks%20of%20air%20strikes%20had%20topped%205%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20pounded%20hundreds%20of%20targets%20in%20Gaza%20from%20the%20air%20on%20Monday%20as%20its%20soldiers%20fought%20Hamas%20militants%20during%20raids%20into%20the%20besieged%20Palestinian%20strip%20where%20civilians%20are%20trapped%20in%20harrowing%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20on%20Monday%20said%20it%20had%20freed%20two%20Israeli%20women%20among%20the%20more%20than%20200%20hostages%20taken%20during%20its%20Oct.%207%20rampage%20in%20southern%20Israel%20in%20which%20the%20Islamist%20group%20killed%201%2C400%20people.%20They%20were%20the%20third%20and%20fourth%20hostages%20to%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20Lieutenant%20General%20Herzi%20Halevi%20issued%20a%20statement%20suggesting%20that%20Israel%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20curbing%20its%20strikes%20on%20the%20densely%20populated%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20hinting%20that%20it%20was%20well%20prepared%20for%20a%20ground%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20bring%20Hamas%20to%20a%20state%20of%20full%20dismantling%2C%26quot%3B%20Halevi%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20path%20is%20a%20path%20of%20unrelenting%20attacks%2C%20damaging%20Hamas%20everywhere%20and%20in%20every%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20well%20prepared%20for%20the%20ground%20operations%20in%20the%20south%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20southern%20Israel%2C%20which%20abuts%20Gaza.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20tactical%2C%20operative%2C%20strategic%20considerations%20that%20have%20provided%20additional%20time%2C%20and%20troops%20who%20have%20more%20time%20are%20better%20prepared%2C%20and%20that%20is%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20public%2C%20the%20United%20States%20has%20stressed%20Israel's%20right%20to%20defend%20itself%20but%20two%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Pentagon%20and%20State%20Department%20have%20stepped%20up%20private%20appeals%20for%20caution%20in%20conversations%20with%20the%20Israelis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20U.S.%20priority%20is%20to%20gain%20time%20for%20negotiations%20to%20free%20other%20hostages%2C%20said%20the%20sources%2C%20who%20spoke%20before%20the%20hostage%20releases%20were%20announced%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20U.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20said%3A%20%26quot%3B%26quot%3BWe%20should%20have%20those%20hostages%20released%20and%20then%20we%20can%20talk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EObama%20Warns%20Israel%20Against%20Civilian%20Casualties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EObama%2C%20in%20a%20rare%20comment%20by%20a%20former%20U.S.%20president%20on%20a%20foreign%20policy%20crisis%2C%20issued%20a%20written%20statement%20warning%20Israel%20not%20to%20cause%20so%20many%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20retaliating%20against%20Hamas%20that%20it%20would%20alienate%20generations%20of%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20Israeli%20military%20strategy%20that%20ignores%20the%20human%20costs%20could%20ultimately%20backfire.%20Already%2C%20thousands%20of%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%2C%20many%20of%20them%20children.%20Hundreds%20of%20thousands%20have%20been%20forced%20from%20their%20homes%2C%26quot%3B%20Obama%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20immediately%20clear%20whether%20Obama%20coordinated%20his%20statement%20with%20Biden%2C%20who%20was%20his%20vice%20president.%20The%20White%20House%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Israeli%20government's%20decision%20to%20cut%20off%20food%2C%20water%20and%20electricity%20to%20a%20captive%20civilian%20population%20threatens%20not%20only%20to%20worsen%20a%20growing%20humanitarian%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20could%20further%20harden%20Palestinian%20attitudes%20for%20generations%2C%20erode%20global%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%20play%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20Israel's%20enemies%2C%20and%20undermine%20long%20term%20efforts%20to%20achieve%20peace%20and%20stability%20in%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20statement%20published%20in%20Medium%20that%20also%20condemned%20Hamas'%20attack%20and%20reiterated%20his%20support%20for%20Israel's%20right%20to%20defend%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Gaza's%20health%20ministry%20said%20436%20people%20had%20been%20killed%20in%20bombardments%20over%20the%20last%2024%20hours%2C%20most%20in%20the%20south%20of%20the%20coastal%20enclave%20next%20to%20which%20Israeli%20troops%20and%20tanks%20have%20massed%20for%20a%20possible%20ground%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20it%20had%20struck%20more%20than%20320%20targets%20in%20Gaza%20over%2024%20hours%2C%20including%20a%20tunnel%20housing%20Hamas%20fighters%2C%20dozens%20of%20command%20and%20lookout%20posts%2C%20and%20mortar%20and%20anti-tank%20missile%20launcher%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20least%205%2C087%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20two%20weeks%20of%20strikes%2C%20including%202%2C055%20children%2C%20the%20health%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20bombardment%20was%20triggered%20by%20the%20Oct.%207%20assault%2C%20the%20bloodiest%20episode%20in%20a%20single%20day%20since%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20was%20founded%2075%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20Gaza's%202.3%20million%20people%20running%20short%20of%20basics%2C%20European%20leaders%20looked%20set%20to%20follow%20the%20United%20Nations%20and%20Arab%20nations%20in%20calling%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bhumanitarian%20pause%26quot%3B%20in%20hostilities%20so%20aid%20could%20reach%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20convoy%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20trucks%20delivered%20water%2C%20food%20and%20medicine%20to%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20on%20Monday%20-%20the%20third%20since%20aid%20began%20flowing%20on%20Saturday%20-%20but%20the%20United%20Nations%20said%20fuel%20was%20not%20included%20and%20reserves%20will%20run%20out%20within%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20U.N.%20said%20desperate%20Gazans%20also%20lacked%20places%20to%20shelter%20from%20the%20unrelenting%20pounding%20that%20has%20flattened%20swathes%20of%20the%20Hamas-ruled%20enclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20meanwhile%20was%20escalating%20beyond%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20aircraft%20hit%20positions%20in%20south%20Lebanon%20held%20by%20Hezbollah%20which%2C%20like%20Hamas%2C%20is%20a%20group%20allied%20to%20Israel's%20long-time%20foe%20Iran.%20The%20Israeli%20army%20and%20Palestinians%20clashed%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%20and%20Hamas%20fired%20more%20rockets%20into%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas's%20armed%20wing%2C%20the%20Izz%20el-Deen%20al-Qassam%20Brigades%2C%20said%20its%20fighters%20engaged%20with%20an%20Israeli%20force%20that%20infiltrated%20southern%20Gaza%2C%20destroying%20two%20bulldozers%20and%20a%20tank%20and%20forcing%20the%20raiders%20to%20withdraw.%20Israel%20made%20no%20comment%20on%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698119220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F6j54gr9_israeli-soldiers-reuters_625x300_23_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-military-vows-unrelenting-attacks-on-hamas-as-war-rages-4508569%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel's%20military%20said%20it%20was%20preparing%20for%20%26quot%3Bunrelenting%20attacks%26quot%3B%20to%20dismantle%20Hamas%20while%20former%20U.S.%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20warned%20that%20%26quot%3Bany%20Israeli%20military%20strategy%20that%20ignores%20the%20human%20costs%20could%20ultimately%20backfire.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-military-vows-unrelenting-attacks-on-hamas-as-war-rages-4508569%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-military-vows-unrelenting-attacks-on-hamas-as-war-rages-4508569%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-military-vows-unrelenting-attacks-on-hamas-as-war-rages-4508569%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Does%20it%20Mean%2C%20Today%2C%20to%20Be%20'With%20Israel'%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24091521%2Fchurch-of-the-holy-sepulchre-9292.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20with%20Israel.%E2%80%9D%20What%20is%20the%20meaning%20of%20this%20assertion%3F%20And%20can%20anyone%20deny%20this%3F%20What%20is%20a%20country%20but%20its%20people%3F%20Why%20should%20anyone%20have%20any%20hesitation%20in%20being%20with%20any%20people%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20being%20with%20Israel%20today%20means%20being%20against%20Palestine.%20It%20has%20been%20accepted%20that%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%98Long%20live%20Israel%E2%80%99%20will%20mean%20%E2%80%98Down%20with%20Palestine%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20a%20strange%20thing%20that%20today%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20be%20it%20France%20or%20England%2C%20the%20US%20or%20Germany%2C%20Turkey%20or%20Africa%2C%20streets%20are%20reverberating%20with%20slogans%20like%20%E2%80%98We%20are%20Palestine%E2%80%99.%20Thousands%20and%20lakhs%20of%20people%20in%20these%20countries%20are%20holding%20the%20Palestinian%20flag.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20governments%20of%20these%20countries%20are%20hoisting%20the%20Israeli%20flag%20on%20their%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20governments%20are%20threatening%20those%20who%20utter%20the%20word%20Palestine%20with%20punishment.%20But%20their%20people%20are%20thumbing%20their%20noses%20at%20this%20threat%20and%20raising%20slogans%20on%20the%20streets%3A%20%E2%80%98From%20river%20to%20the%20sea%2C%20Palestine%20will%20be%20free.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EObjection%20has%20been%20raised%20to%20this%20slogan%20in%20England.%20The%20meaning%20of%20this%20slogan%20is%20the%20denial%20of%20the%20existence%20of%20Israel%2C%20this%20is%20the%20allegation.%20People%20participating%20in%20the%20procession%20said%2C%20when%20we%20raise%20this%20slogan%2C%20we%20do%20not%20talk%20about%20destroying%20Israel%2C%20we%20only%20demand%20the%20freedom%20of%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20had%20to%20choose%20between%20these%20two%2C%20what%20would%20one%20choose%3F%20Does%20the%20flag%20of%20a%20country%20look%20good%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20people%20or%20in%20government%20offices%3F%20What%20would%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20themselves%20feel%3F%20Do%20they%20consider%20it%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%20that%20the%20unarmed%20people%20across%20the%20world%20have%20the%20flag%20of%20Palestine%20in%20their%20hands%20and%20the%20anthem%20of%20Palestine%20on%20their%20lips%20but%20Israel%20exists%20only%20in%20the%20statements%20of%20armed%20governments%3F%20Which%20one%20of%20the%20two%20should%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%20for%20any%20people%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20would%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20feel%20seeing%20the%20colours%20of%20Palestine%20on%20the%20streets%20around%20the%20world%3F%20Would%20they%20be%20feeling%20lonely%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20First%20Sights%20and%20Sounds%20of%20War%3A%20Notes%20from%20Israel-Palestine%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-diary-gaza-occupation%5C%22%3EThe%20First%20Sights%20and%20Sounds%20of%20War%3A%20Notes%20from%20Israel-Palestine%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20who%20is%20with%20Palestine%20should%20probably%20say%20that%20he%20is%20with%20Israel%20also.%20The%20right%20to%20life%20of%20these%20two%20people%20are%20not%20and%20should%20not%20be%20mutually%20exclusive.%20Which%20means%20the%20right%20to%20live%20with%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Palestinians%20do%20not%20have%20dignity%2C%20the%20Israelis%20feel%20insecure%20because%20it%20is%20in%20their%20name%20that%20the%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20robbed%20of%20their%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20does%20it%20mean%20to%20be%20with%20Israel%3F%20Who%20is%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20well-wisher%20at%20this%20time%3F%20The%20one%20that%20is%20pushing%20Israel%20deeper%20into%20the%20closed%20tunnel%20of%20war%20and%20violence%3F%20Or%20the%20one%20who%20is%20warning%20it%20that%20this%20tunnel%20is%20closed%20from%20the%20front%20and%20entering%20it%20means%20being%20trapped%20in%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWho%20is%20really%20with%20Israel%3F%20All%20those%20people%20who%20echo%20the%20Israeli%20government%E2%80%99s%20shout%20for%20revenge%20for%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attack%3F%20Those%20who%20support%20or%20are%20silent%20after%20the%20Israeli%20government%20murdered%20more%20than%204%2C500%20people%20in%20Gaza%20and%20pulverised%20it%3F%20Or%20those%20who%20are%20still%20saying%20that%20the%20answer%20to%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20is%20not%20to%20destroy%20Gaza%3F%20They%20ask%20Israel%20not%20be%20hotheaded%20as%20it%20has%20always%20been%2C%20and%20use%20this%20opportunity%20with%20a%20cool%20mind%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20vicious%20cycle%20of%20violence%20in%20which%20Israel%20has%20put%20itself%20and%20the%20Palestinians%20along%20with%20it%20for%20the%20last%2075%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20are%20all%20those%20people%20and%20their%20leaders%20like%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20who%20came%20running%20to%20embrace%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20criminal%20thoroughly%20discredited%20and%20war%20hungry%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20well-wishers%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIs%20their%20priority%20the%20release%20of%20more%20than%20200%20people%20held%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%3F%20When%20the%20Israeli%20government%20started%20bombing%20Gaza%2C%20did%20it%20have%20these%20people%2C%20its%20own%20people%20in%20mind%2C%20who%20could%20be%20killed%20in%20this%20bombing%3F%20Instead%20of%20this%20bombing%2C%20would%20it%20not%20have%20been%20better%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20negotiate%20with%20Hamas%20and%20first%20free%20these%20hostages%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBe%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fopinion%2F2023-10-10%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Farriving-again-at-the-cycle-of-vengeance%2F0000018b-15d7-d2fc-a59f-d5df4d810000%5C%22%3EAmira%20Hass%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fvideo-gideon-levy-karan-thapar-gaza-israel-palestine%5C%22%3EGideon%20Levy%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nybooks.com%2Fonline%2F2023%2F10%2F11%2Fdeja-vu-in-israel%2F%5C%22%3EDavid%20Shulma%3C%2Fa%3En%2C%20hundreds%2C%20thousands%20of%20Israelis%20are%20shouting%20that%20if%20Israel%20wants%20a%20life%20of%20peace%20then%20it%20will%20have%20to%20liberate%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20former%20advisor%20Daniel%20Levy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fprogram%2Fthe-bottom-line%2F2023%2F10%2F21%2Fwhy-does-the-us-not-support-a-ceasefire-in-gaza%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20his%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20before%20condemning%20the%20attack%20by%20Hamas%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20ask%20the%20fundamental%20question%2C%20how%20did%20we%20all%20reach%20this%20point%3F%20Why%20are%20we%20forced%20to%20ask%20this%20question%3F%20Levy%20said%20that%20the%20need%20to%20ask%20this%20question%20would%20not%20arise%20if%20millions%20of%20Palestinians%20had%20not%20been%20crushed%20every%20day%20for%2075%20years%20in%20a%20tight%20space%20in%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20cruel%20prisons.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20is%20not%20why%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20system%20failed%20and%20why%20it%20was%20not%20even%20aware%20of%20such%20long%20preparations%20by%20Hamas.%20The%20real%20question%20is%20who%20made%20Hamas%20powerful%3F%20Why%20did%20Israeli%20governments%2C%20and%20Netanyahu%20in%20particular%2C%20pit%20Hamas%20against%20Fatah%3F%20Why%20did%20Israel%20refuse%20to%20honour%20even%20the%20Oslo%20Agreement%2C%20and%20why%20did%20it%20continue%20to%20steal%20Palestinian%20land%20under%20the%20watchful%20eye%20of%20the%20US%2C%20continue%20killing%20Palestinians%20and%20humiliating%20them%20on%20an%20hourly%20basis%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20who%20created%20such%20a%20situation%20that%20Israel%20has%20to%20see%20Hamas%20in%20every%20Palestinian%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Levy%20cautions%20that%20even%20after%20razing%20Gaza%2C%20Israel%20will%20never%20have%20more%20security%20than%20it%20has%20today.%20The%20only%20guarantee%20of%20the%20security%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20is%20a%20free%20Palestine.%20When%20you%20suppress%20someone%2C%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20increasing%20that%20pressure%20because%20the%20desire%20of%20the%20person%20being%20suppressed%20to%20raise%20his%20head%20increases%20in%20the%20same%20proportion.%20Then%20you%20are%20always%20alert%2C%20putting%20a%20lot%20of%20your%20energy%20into%20increasing%20that%20pressure%20to%20keep%20him%20under%20your%20boot.%20It%E2%80%99s%20better%20to%20get%20off%20his%20back%20and%20let%20him%20walk%20straight.%20Then%20you%20too%20will%20be%20able%20to%20walk%20peacefully%20next%20to%20him.%20It%20is%20just%20that%20simple.%20If%20Israel%20wants%20peace%20then%20it%20will%20have%20to%20give%20freedom%20to%20the%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EApoorvanand%20teaches%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698119189000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24091521%2Fchurch-of-the-holy-sepulchre-9292.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhat-does-it-mean-today-to-be-with-israel%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20Israel%20wants%20peace%20then%20it%20will%20have%20to%20give%20freedom%20to%20the%20Palestinians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhat-does-it-mean-today-to-be-with-israel%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ferocious%20breeds%20of%20dog%20set%20to%20be%20banned%20in%20this%20state%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698119150000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104665158%2Cimgsize-36494.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fgoa%2Fstate-to-ban-ferocious-breeds-of-