%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fsag-aftra-strike-studios-new-offer-streaming-residuals-1235765718%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fsag-aftra-strike-studios-new-offer-streaming-residuals-1235765718%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fsag-aftra-strike-studios-new-offer-streaming-residuals-1235765718%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20Bowled%20to%20Deceive%20but%2C%20Frank%20and%20Big-Hearted%2C%20Was%20the%20Least%20Deceptive%20of%20Men%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24083056%2FF9Hm3y3W0AAny2G.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20certain%20genus%20of%20cricketers%20%E2%80%93%20an%20elite%20of%20the%20elite%20%E2%80%93%20who%20are%20not%20only%20supreme%20at%20their%20skill%20but%20somehow%20seem%20to%20embody%20it%20altogether.%20Shane%20Warne%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20leg%20spin%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20exponent%3B%20to%20bowling%2C%20he%20somehow%20brought%20the%20full%20force%20of%20his%20vibrant%20personality.%20Wasim%20Akram%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20merely%20the%20left-arm%20pace%20bowler%20supreme%2C%20but%20an%20encyclopedist%20of%20the%20craft%2C%20the%20master%20of%20all%20its%20aspects%20and%20dimensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20formed%20part%20of%20this%20club.%20He%20was%20left-arm%20slow%20bowling.%20He%20was%20its%20greatest%20champion%20and%20its%20most%20joyous%20ambassador.%20He%20bowled%20it%20on%20the%20field%3B%20he%20bowled%20it%20in%20his%20head%3B%20he%20bowled%20it%20into%20eternity.%20Once%20you%20saw%20him%2C%20he%20became%20the%20benchmark%2C%20the%20reference%20point%20for%20all%20other%20practitioners.%20He%20wakened%20you%20to%20its%20possibilities%2C%20and%20once%20wakened%20you%20never%20forgot%20them.%20More%20than%2040%20years%20have%20elapsed%20since%20he%20bowled%2C%20but%20he%20led%20me%20on%20to%20other%20favourites%20like%20Ravi%20Shastri%2C%20Daniel%20Vettori%20and%20Rangana%20Herath%2C%20and%20I%20fancy%20I%20still%20see%20him%20when%20I%20watch%20Ravi%20Jadeja%2C%20or%20Mitchell%20Santner.%20He%20also%20brought%20a%20unique%20spirit%20to%20cricket%20%E2%80%93%20an%20expansiveness%20and%20chivalry.%20He%20bowled%20to%20deceive%20but%2C%20frank%20and%20big-hearted%2C%20was%20the%20least%20deceptive%20of%20men.%20To%20face%20him%20must%20have%20been%20like%20having%20your%20pocket%20picked%20then%20being%20given%20your%20wallet%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThree%20times%20did%20Bishan%20tour%20Australia%3A%20as%20a%20young%20man%20in%201967-68%2C%20as%20a%20colourful%20guest%20in%20the%20Rest%20of%20the%20World%20XI%20in%201971-2%2C%20and%20as%20captain%20and%20guru%20in%201977-78.%20On%20that%20last%20trip%2C%20Indian%20brought%20their%20fabled%20four%20spinners%2C%20as%20complete%20an%20ensemble%20as%20has%20equipped%20any%20team%3A%20not%20just%20their%20skipper%20but%20gnomic%20Prasanna%2C%20crafty%20Venkat%2C%20and%20Chandra%2C%20sui%20generis.%20We%20tend%20to%20remember%20that%20Chandra%20took%2012%20on%20a%20dark%2C%20pebbly%20pitch%20at%20the%20MCG%2C%20but%20Bishan%20also%20took%2012%E2%80%A6in%20Perth%E2%80%A6at%20the%20WACA.%20Can%20you%20credit%20it%3F%20The%20world%E2%80%99s%20slowest%20bowler%20on%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20fastest%20pitch%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20breeziest%20ground.%20To%20a%20boy%2C%20as%20I%20was%2C%20this%20was%20a%20kind%20of%20revelation%3A%20how%20much%20subtlety%20and%20variety%20could%20be%20wrung%20from%20a%20physique%20that%20testified%20to%20an%20enjoyment%20of%20earthy%20pleasures%2C%20an%20approach%20so%20seemingly%20artless%2C%20and%20an%20arc%20like%20an%20angler%E2%80%99s%20cast.%20It%20was%20intensified%20by%20Bishan%E2%80%99s%20seeming%20indifference%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20cricket.%20He%20hoicked%20earthily%3B%20he%20treated%20fielding%20as%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20chore.%20But%20in%20an%20over%20of%20Bishan%E2%80%99s%2C%20he%20made%20the%20world%20stand%20still%2C%20almost%20on%20tip-toe.%20The%20ball%20took%20so%20long%20in%20its%20path%2C%20time%20enough%20for%20thoughts%20to%20rush%20through%20a%20batter%E2%80%99s%20head%3B%20yet%20it%20was%20almost%20always%20a%20cardinal%20error%20to%20commit%20too%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBeaten%20in%20two%20squeakers%2C%20India%20just%20lost%20that%20series%20%E2%80%93%20imagine%20had%20they%20pulled%20it%20off%2C%20more%20than%2040%20years%20before%20Virat%20Kohli%E2%80%99s%20men%20of%202018-19.%20Remarkably%2C%20perhaps%2C%20I%20suspect%20that%20few%20Australians%20would%20have%20begrudged%20them.%20More%20powerful%20teams%20have%20visited%20our%20shores%2C%20but%20none%20so%20completely%20charming%3A%20valiant%20Mohinder%2C%20soulful%20Vishwanath%2C%20suave%20Vengsarkar%2C%20loveable%20Kirmani.%20It%20is%20incredible%20to%20think%20how%20long%20they%20stayed%2C%20all%20summer%2C%20and%20how%20far%20they%20travelled%2C%20through%20Mt%20Gambier.%20They%20came%20to%20my%20home%20town%2C%20a%20white%20bread%20industrial%20city%20called%20Geelong%2C%20where%20they%20trussed%20up%20the%20local%20XI.%20They%20felt%20like%20part%20of%20us%2C%20fascinating%20house%20guests%2C%20whom%20you%E2%80%99d%20have%20been%20happy%20to%20stay%20forever.%20Who%20of%20us%20in%20Australia%20had%20ever%20seen%20a%20patka%20before%2C%20such%20as%20those%20Bishan%20coiled%20around%20his%20head%3F%20Mind%20you%2C%20he%20could%20have%20bowled%20in%20a%20trilby%20and%20been%20just%20as%20entrancing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20no%20fluke%2C%20I%20think%2C%20that%20Bishan%20is%20the%20subject%20of%20some%20of%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20best%20photographs.%20There%20was%20a%20feeling%20of%20a%20mystery%20to%20be%20unlocked%2C%20if%20you%20could%20just%20stop%20time%20long%20enough%20to%20study%20closely.%20There%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fphoto%2Fbishen-bedi-photographed-by-ken-kelly-in-1974-234198%3FobjectId%3D26875%5C%22%3EKen%20Kelly%E2%80%99s%20vivid%20close-up%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20signature%20detail%20of%20Bishan%20imparting%20to%20the%20ball%20with%20his%20right%20thumb%20a%20last%20unconscious%20nudge%20into%20his%20left%20hand.%20There%E2%80%99s%20Adrian%20Murrell%E2%80%99s%20study%20of%20him%20warming%20up%2C%20only%20the%20whites%20of%20his%20eyes%20visible%2C%20as%20though%20lost%20in%20tantric%20contemplation.%20There%E2%80%99s%20Patrick%20Eagar%E2%80%99s%20side-on%20snap%20at%20Lord%E2%80%99s%20which%20captures%20Bedi%20connected%20to%20the%20ground%20only%20by%20the%20outside%20of%20the%20toe%20of%20his%20left%20boot%2C%20like%20a%20hot%20air%20balloon%20straining%20at%20its%20moorings.%20Seeing%20an%20Eagar%20sequence%20of%20Bedi%20in%20a%20copy%20of%20MCC%20Masterclass%20so%20inspired%20another%20young%20Sikh%2C%20Monty%20Panesar%2C%20that%20he%20committed%20to%20a%20lifetime%20in%20the%20same%20genre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24083208%2FF9JMon9WoAAF2wq.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24083208%2FF9JMon9WoAAF2wq.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24083208%2FF9JMon9WoAAF2wq-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681470%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBishan%20Singh%20Bedi.%20Photo%3A%20Shared%20on%20X%20by%20%40SonuSood%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESomething%20about%20the%20very%20memory%20of%20Bishan%20pricks%20you%20about%20directions%20the%20game%20has%20taken.%20Can%20you%20conceive%20of%20him%20in%20an%20auction%3F%20He%20was%20not%20to%20be%20bought%20and%20sold.%20Can%20you%20imagine%20the%20fatuity%20of%20putting%20a%20number%20and%20his%20name%20on%20the%20back%20of%20his%20shirt%3F%20It%20would%20have%20been%20like%20an%20explanatory%20caption%20on%20the%20Mona%20Lisa.%20He%20also%20belonged%20also%20to%20a%20now-forgotten%20species%20of%20cricketers%20%E2%80%93%20those%20rebel%20souls%20of%20the%201970s%20who%20were%20often%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20their%20administrative%20classes.%20Bishan%20was%20the%20Indian%20counterpart%20of%20Ian%20Chappell%20and%20Dennis%20Lillee%20in%20Australia%20and%20John%20Snow%20and%20Tony%20Greig%20in%20England.%20Today%E2%80%99s%20cricketers%2C%20memorable%20and%20exciting%20as%20they%20may%20be%2C%20are%20in%20the%20main%20pampered%20yes%20men%2C%20who%20never%20speak%20out%20of%20turn%2C%20lest%20they%20upset%20a%20brand%2C%20roil%20social%20media.%20They%20are%20represented%20by%20agents%20and%20unions%2C%20firewalled%20by%20entourages.%20Imagine%20the%20courage%20it%20once%20took%20to%20resist%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20overlords%2C%20its%20self-constituting%20national%20monopolies%2C%20not%20least%20the%20stern%20and%20reproving%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20to%20be%20one-out%20against%20leviathan%2C%20usually%20running%20the%20gauntlet%20of%20the%20press%2C%20and%20in%20doing%20so%20courting%20the%20suspicion%20of%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuresh%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20wonderful%20biography%2C%20%3Cem%3EBishan%3A%20Portrait%20of%20a%20Cricketer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20collates%20a%20host%20of%20confrontations%20with%20the%20BCCI.%20During%20one%20Nagpur%20Test%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20BCCI%20stuck%20Bishan%E2%80%99s%20team%20not%20in%20a%20hotel%20but%20in%20an%20MLA%20Hostel%20in%20which%20only%20he%20and%20the%20team%20manager%20had%20running%20water.%20Bishan%20remonstrated%20so%20fiercely%20with%20the%20local%20official%20that%20he%20was%20arraigned%20to%20appear%20before%20a%20BCCI%20disciplinary%20committee%20%E2%80%93%20sitting%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20in%20a%20five-star%20hotel%20in%20Mumbai.%20Having%20been%20reprimanded%2C%20Bishan%20learned%20that%20the%20BCCI%20had%20not%20booked%20his%20return%20tickets%20to%20Chandigarh%2C%20and%20there%20were%20no%20seats%20on%20the%20train.%20So%20it%20was%20that%20the%20captain%20of%20India%20travelled%20to%20a%20Duleep%20Trophy%20game%20bunked%20in%20a%20luggage%20rack%20for%201400%20km%2C%20then%20took%20a%20bus%20the%20last%20250%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99ve%20called%20him%20Bishan%20here%20advisedly%2C%20because%20I%20did%20have%20the%20good%20fortune%20to%20know%20him%2C%20just%20a%20little%2C%20although%20with%20him%20it%20always%20felt%20like%20more.%20Such%20was%20his%20immediate%20warmth%3B%20it%20was%20like%20being%20wrapped%20in%20an%20instant%20hug.%20%E2%80%98You%20and%20Ray%20Robinson!%E2%80%99%20he%20said%20when%20we%20were%20first%20introduced%20in%20England%2015%20years%20ago.%20%E2%80%98My%20favourite%20Australian%20writers!%E2%80%99%20And%20much%20as%20I%20liked%20being%20recognised%2C%20I%20was%20the%20more%20chuffed%20by%20his%20reference%20to%20Ray%20Robbie%2C%20likewise%20my%20favourite%2C%20and%20something%20of%20a%20personal%20hero.%20Bishan%20had%20a%20capacity%20for%20immediate%2C%20easy%20intimacy%2C%20and%20a%20fund%20of%20earthy%20opinions%20expressed%20with%20an%20absolute%20unguardedness%2C%20whether%20about%20his%20reverence%20for%20the%20Nawab%20of%20Pataudi%20Junior%2C%20his%20ambivalent%20relations%20with%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%2C%20or%20his%20utter%20contempt%20for%20administrators%20generally.%20No%20coaching%20sinecure%20or%20commentator%E2%80%99s%20blazer%20for%20Bishan.%20He%20was%20absolutely%20his%20own%20man%2C%20proudly%20Indian%2C%20utterly%20cosmopolitan.%20Had%20the%20Australian%20Arthur%20Mailey%20not%20said%20already%20said%20it%2C%20after%20being%20criticised%20for%20advising%20the%20Englishman%20Ian%20Peebles%20in%201930%2C%20the%20remark%20could%20have%20come%20from%20Bishan%3A%20%E2%80%98Spin%20bowling%20is%20an%20art%2C%20and%20art%20is%20international.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20dearly%20beloved%20he%20was%20too.%20I%20once%20had%20a%20night%20out%20with%20him%20at%20Delhi%20Golf%20Club%2C%20where%20he%20received%20a%20non-stop%20stream%20of%20well-wishers%20and%20petitioners%20as%20though%20they%20were%20personal%20friends%20%E2%80%93%20only%20to%20quietly%20confide%20that%20he%20had%20only%20the%20vaguest%20idea%20whom%20half%20of%20them%20were.%20When%20we%20came%20out%2C%20I%20thought%20that%20my%20driver%20was%20going%20to%20faint%20with%20excitement.%20%E2%80%98Naveen%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20so%20sorry%20to%20have%20kept%20you%20so%20late%2C%E2%80%99%20I%20said%20as%20we%20returned%20to%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%98Sir!%E2%80%99%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%98It%20was%20Bishan%20Bedi.%E2%80%99%20I%20had%20to%20pinch%20myself%20too.%20Good%20heavens%2C%20it%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGideon%20Haigh%20has%20been%20a%20journalist%20for%20almost%20four%20decades%2C%20has%20published%20more%20than%2040%20books%20and%20contributed%20to%20more%20than%20100%20newspapers%20and%20magazines.%20He%20is%20also%20co-host%20of%20the%20podcast%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3ECricket%2C%20Et%20Cetera.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698116944000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24083056%2FF9Hm3y3W0AAny2G.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbishan-singh-bedi-bowled-to-deceive-but-frank-and-big-hearted-was-the-least-deceptive-of-men%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20brought%20a%20unique%20spirit%20to%20cricket%20%E2%80%93%20an%20expansiveness%20and%20chivalry.%20To%20face%20him%20must%20have%20been%20like%20having%20your%20pocket%20picked%20then%20given%20your%20wallet%20back.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbishan-singh-bedi-bowled-to-deceive-but-frank-and-big-hearted-was-the-least-dece