ing%20he%20owns%20the%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Esuperyacht%20instead.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20attorneys%20want%20to%20have%20a%20Russian%20oligarch's%20%24300%20million%20superyacht%20forfeited%20to%20the%20US%2C%20over%20a%20year%20after%20it%20was%20first%20seized%20by%20Fiji%20authorities%20after%20the%20war%20with%20Ukraine%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Attorney%20Damian%20Williams%20on%20Monday%20filed%20a%20civil%20forfeiture%20complaint%20against%20the%20Amadea%2C%20an%20extravagant%20348-foot-long%20luxury%20ship%20that%20US%20officials%20allege%20is%20owned%20by%20billionaire%20Suleiman%20Kerimov.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Amadea%20features%20a%20helicopter%20pad%20on%20its%20foredeck%2C%20a%20mosaic-lined%20swimming%20pool%20at%20the%20rear%2C%20fire%20pits%2C%20and%20an%20indoor%20movie%20theater%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.charterworld.com%2Findex.html%3Fsub%3Dyacht-charter%26charter%3Dmotor-yacht-amadea-10526%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20CharterWorld%20Luxury%20Yacht%20Charters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKerimov%20was%20initially%20sanctioned%20in%202018%20over%20his%20ties%20to%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20Williams%20wrote%20in%20court%20filings.%20Yet%20in%202021%2C%20he%20worked%20out%20a%20deal%20to%20buy%20the%20yacht%20through%20a%20series%20of%20corporate%20entities%20to%20obscure%20who%20owned%20the%20vessel%20and%20violated%20sanctions%20by%20having%20more%20than%20%241%20million%20in%20maintenance%20work%20done%20on%20the%20ship%2C%20the%20court%20documents%20allege.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20yacht%20was%20initially%20seized%20by%20Fiji%20authorities%20after%20it%20raced%20into%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20when%20the%20war%20with%20Ukraine%20broke%20out%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-63297797%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20BBC%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20November%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20prosecutor%20Andrew%20Adams%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20authorities%20noticed%20the%20vessel%20%26quot%3Bscrambling%20out%20of%20waters%20where%20we%20would%20normally%20be%20able%20to%20seize%20it%26quot%3B%20just%20weeks%20after%20Russian%20forces%20invaded%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEssentially%2C%20the%20boat%20tried%20to%20go%20dark%2C%26quot%3B%20Adams%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20reported%20that%20US%20officials%20believed%20the%20ship%20was%20going%20to%20race%20for%20Vladivostok%2C%20a%20Russian%20port%20near%20North%20Korea%2C%20when%20it%20was%20seized%20in%20Fiji.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ship%20was%20then%20seized%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20and%20moved%20to%20California%20where%20it%20remains%20docked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20lawyers%20for%20a%20separate%20Russian%20oligarch%20claiming%20to%20own%20the%20yacht%20%E2%80%94%20Eduard%20Khudainatov%2C%20who%20hasn't%20been%20sanctioned%20%E2%80%94%20filed%20legal%20papers%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuperyacht-sanction-russia-ukraine-fiji-amadea-suleyman-kerimov-khudainatov-millemarin-2022-4%5C%22%3EFiji%20court%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20seeking%20to%20have%20the%20boat%20turned%20back%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhudainatov's%20lawyers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-10-23%2Fus-seeks-forfeiture-of-russian-tycoon-s-300-million-superyacht%3Fsrnd%3Dpremium-asia%26leadSource%3Duverify%2520wall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they've%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20in%20San%20Diego%2C%20California%20as%20well%20seeking%20to%20get%20the%20superyacht%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Khudainatov's%20lawyers%20referred%20Insider%20to%20the%20filing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20wrangling%20surrounding%20the%20Amadea%20underscores%20the%20challenges%20over%20determining%20the%20actual%20owner%20of