or%20costs%20a%20lot%20less%2C%20too.%20For%20reference%2C%20the%20most%20affordable%20new%20iPad%20sells%20for%20around%20%24400%2C%20and%20that's%20on%20sale%2C%20whereas%20the%20most%20affordable%20new%20Kindle%20Fire%20tablets%20cost%20less%20than%20%2475.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGranted%2C%20iPads%20have%20some%20features%20and%20functions%20Fire%20tablets%20don't%2C%20like%20the%20ability%20to%20run%20certain%20notable%20apps.%20Overall%2C%20the%20Fire%20tablet%20is%20a%20capable%20and%20affordable%20device%20that%20will%20suit%20the%20needs%20of%20most%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Amazon%20Fire%20tablet%20used%20for%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fire%20tablet%20can%20be%20used%20for%20all%20the%20standard%20things%20you'd%20expect%2C%20from%20browsing%20the%20web%20to%20watching%20videos%2C%20checking%20emails%2C%20and%20playing%20games.%20You%20can%20use%20it%20to%20read%20ebooks%2C%C2%A0%20doodle%2C%20play%20music%2C%20and%20so%20much%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20an%20Amazon%20Fire%20tablet%20can%20do%20almost%20everything%20any%20other%20tablet%20can%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20is%20the%20newest%20Amazon%20Fire%20tablet%20model%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Amazon%20Fire%20Max%2011%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20this%20tablet%20series.%20The%20Fire%20Max%2011%20has%204%20GB%20of%20RAM%2C%20and%20is%20available%20with%20128%20GB%20of%20storage%20space%20that%20can%20be%20expanded%20to%20a%20terabyte%20with%20a%20micro%20SD%20card%2C%C2%A0%20a%2014-hour%20battery%2C%20a%20sharp%20screen%2C%20and%20a%20solid%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fire%20Max%2011%20is%20hardly%20the%20only%20Fire%20tablet%20in%20town.%20There%20are%20several%20others%20worth%20considering.%20These%20include%20the%20Amazon%20Fire%20HD%2010%20Kids%20tablet%2C%20which%20is%20built%20to%20be%20extra%20durable%2C%20it%20has%20a%2010.1%26quot%3B%20high%20def%20display%20and%203%20GB%20of%20RAM.%20It%20can%20be%20overseen%20and%20controlled%20by%20a%20parent%20control%20center%20on%20a%20linked%20smartphone%20or%20tablet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20adults%20looking%20for%20a%20less%20expensive%20but%20capable%20tablet%2C%20go%20back%20one%20generation%20to%20the%20Fire%20HD%2010%20Plus%20tablet%2C%20which%20has%204%20GB%20of%20RAM%20and%20either%2032%20or%2064%20GB%20of%20storage%20behind%20a%20crisp%20display.%20It%20works%20with%20myriad%20apps%20like%20Netflix%2C%20Spotify%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-now-lets-you-listen-to-music-free-on-smartphones-on-tv-and-online-2019-11%5C%22%3EAmazon%20Music%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you%20want%20a%20smaller%20tablet%20perfect%20for%20travel%2C%20the%20Amazon%20Fire%20HD%208%20Plus%20has%20an%208-inch%20screen%20and%20weighs%20in%20at%20just%209.9%20ounces.%20Its%2010-hour%20battery%20life%20will%20entertain%20you%20for%20the%20whole%20plane%20ride%20or%20during%20your%20daily%20train%20commute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20disadvantages%20of%20an%20Amazon%20Fire%20tablet%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20many%20people%20bemoan%20about%20the%20Fire%20tablet%20is%20the%20mediocre-at-best%20camera.%20Another%20is%20that%20you%20are%20limited%20to%20using%20the%20native%20web%20browser%20loaded%20on%20the%20tablet%2C%20which%20is%20called%20Silk%20and%20has%20a%20worse%20user%20experience%20than%20Chrome%2C%20Firefox%2C%20Safari%2C%20or%20your%20other%20favorites.%20And%20the%20other%20native%20apps%2C%20like%20the%20maps%20and%20calculator%2C%20pale%20in%20quality%20to%20those%20you'd%20find%20on%2C%20say%2C%20an%20iPhone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20biggest%20drawback%20to%20the%20Fire%20tablet%20is%20its%20limited%20access%20to%20and%20use%20of%20some%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20apps%20out%20there.%20Nearly%20every%20Google%20app%20is%20unavailable%20on%20the%20Fire%20tablet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20tablet%20and%20an%20Amazon%20Fire%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20difference%3A%20The%20Amazon%20Fire%20tablet%20is%20indeed%20a%20tablet%2C%20not%20a%20separate%20category%20of%20devices.%20The%20Fire%20tablet%20is%20manufactured%20by%20the%20Taiwanese%20tech%20company%20Quanta%20Computer.%20While%20the%20Fire%20tablet's%20operating%20system%20differs%20from%20iOS%20and%20Android%2C%20it's%20a%20reliable%20device%20with%20similar%20capabilities%20to%20other%20tablets.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20the%20Amazon%20Fire%20tablet%20have%20an%20internet%20browser%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fire%20tablet%20has%20a%20web%20browser%20called%20Silk.%20It%20works%20much%20like%20any%20other%20browser%2C%20and%20via%20Silk%2C%20you%20can%20navigate%20to%20just%20about%20any%20page%20on%20the%20web%2C%20including%20search%20engines%20like%20Google%20or%20Bing.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20use%20YouTube%20on%20a%20Fire%20tablet%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tablet%20arrives%20already%20configured%2C%20and%20you%20cannot%20immediately%20watch%20YouTube%20because%20it's%20a%20Google%20app%20not%20available%20in%20the%20Amazon%20App%20Store.%20But%20there's%20a%20workaround.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20tablet's%20settings%2C%20configure%20it%20to%20allow%20apps%20from%20%26quot%3BUnknown%26quot%3B%20sources%2C%20then%20download%20the%20YouTube%20app%20onto%20a%20separate%20computer.%20Connect%20the%20tablet%20and%20computer%20via%20USB%20cable%2C%20and%20you%20should%20be%20able%20to%20transfer%20YouTube%20to%20the%20tablet.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20have%20to%20have%20an%20Amazon%20subscription%20to%20use%20a%20Fire%20tablet%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20Amazon%20subscription%20is%20necessary%20to%20use%20an%20Amazon%20Fire%20tablet%20fully.%20Once%20you%20buy%20the%20tablet%2C%20it's%20yours%20%E2%80%94