20in%20June%202022%20said%20they%20planned%20to%20make%20investments%20in%20the%20mobile-network%20technology%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchandmarkets.com%2Freports%2F5531178%2Fglobal-5g-enterprise-market-2021-2031-by%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGMD%20Research%20report%20estimated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2C%20by%202031%2C%20the%20global%205G%20enterprise%20market%20could%20be%20worth%20more%20than%20%2483%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E5G%20is%20the%20latest%20version%20of%20superfast%20mobile%20internet.%20It%20boasts%20higher%20capacity%20and%20speed%20capabilities%20and%20lower%20latency%20than%20the%20previous%20generation%20of%204G%20mobile%20internet%2C%20meaning%20that%20consumers%20can%20now%20use%20mobile%20internet%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20purposes%20in%20business%20and%20personal%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20these%20potential%20benefits%20come%20risks%20that%20companies%20and%20engineers%20must%20carefully%20manage.%20Two%20experts%20in%205G%20technology%20and%20cybersecurity%2C%20Rahim%20Tafazolli%20and%20Alan%20Woodward%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Surrey%2C%20spoke%20to%20Insider%20about%20the%20key%20steps%20organizations%20should%20take%20to%20develop%20a%20secure%205G%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Understand%20your%20needs%20and%20hire%20the%20right%20staff%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20to%20check%20is%20whether%20you%20need%20a%205G%20network%2C%20and%20if%20so%2C%20how%20you%20should%20scope%20it.%20Everything%20from%20traffic%2C%20security%20levels%2C%20and%20latency%20requirements%20will%20determine%20how%20to%20lay%20out%20your%205G%20plans%20safely%20and%20securely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20requires%20trained%20staff%2C%20Tafazolli%2C%20who%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20director%20of%205GIC%2C%206GIC%2C%20and%20the%20Institute%20for%20Communication%20Systems%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Surrey%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20most%20of%20these%20organizations%2C%20they%20are%20not%20telecom%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20IT%20people%2C%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20manage%2C%20maintain%2C%20and%20support%20a%20telecoms%20network%20requires%20telecom%20skills.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Evaluate%20public%20versus%20private%205G%20options%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20full%20complement%20of%20telecom%20skills%20required%2C%20it's%20much%20safer%20to%20rely%20on%20those%20who%20do%20to%20provide%20you%20with%20a%20secure%205G%20network.%20A%20public%205G%20network%20slice%20from%20a%20mobile%20operator%20may%2C%20in%20that%20instance%2C%20be%20better%20than%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flas-vegas-private-5g-network-2023-9%5C%22%3Eprivate%2C%20on-premise%205G%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20you%20have%20to%20maintain%20in-house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETafazolli%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Byou%20don't%20need%20to%20bother%20yourself%20so%20much%20with%20the%20maintenance%20and%20support%20of%20those%20systems%26quot%3B%20by%20choosing%20a%20slice%20of%20a%20preexisting%20public%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Woodward%2C%20a%20cybersecurity%20expert%20and%20a%20visiting%20professor%20at%20the%20Surrey%20Centre%20for%20Cyber%20Security%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bsome%20organizations%20may%20prefer%20a%20private%20network%20under%20their%20own%20control%2C%20despite%20the%20overhead%20of%20managing%20it%2C%20because%20they%20are%20handling%20sensitive%20data%20or%20have%20competitive%20concerns%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20private%20network%20is%20typically%20more%20secure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Use%205G's%20configurable%20security%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20owners%20and%20IT%20leads%20may%20think%20they%20have%20to%20go%20down%20the%20private-network%20route%20because%20of%20security%20concerns.%20But%205G%20is%20a%20fundamentally%20different%20technology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20used%20to%20lay%20fibers%20for%20their%20own%20personal%20high-security%20networks%2C%20they%20would%20want%20their%20own%20'dark'%20fiber%20because%20nobody%20would%20intercept%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Woodward%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20one%20has%20to%20remember%20is%20that%205G%20has%20been%20designed%20with%20security%20from%20the%20start%2C%20all%20the%20way%20up%20from%20the%20IP%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20system%20is%20foolproof%20or%20hack-proof%2C%20of%20course.%20But%20because%205G%20is%20a%20software-defined%20network%2C%20you%20can%20configure%20it%20to%20your%20needs.%20Evaluate%20your%20risks%20and%20use%205G's%20configurability%20to%20build%20the%20appropriate%20mitigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Partner%20with%20experts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20telecoms%20is%20not%20your%20core%20business%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20need%20some%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20Woodward%20said.%20While%205G%20is%20still%20maturing%2C%20experts%20such%20as%20mobile%20operators%20and%20infrastructure%20vendors%20can%20guide%20you%20through%20planning%20and%20deploying%20networks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETafazolli%20said%20that%20as%20well%20as%20accepting%20what%20providers%20offer%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20can%20implement%20your%20own%20security%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20standardized%20security%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20put%20your%20own%20encryption%20against%20the%20mechanism%20for%20possible%20attacks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Implement%20monitoring%20and%20automation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOperating%20a%205G%20network%20requires%20extensive%20telecom%20expertise%20that%20many%20enterprises%20lack.%20But%20there%20are%20tools%20that%20can%20help%20with%20advanced%20monitoring%20and%20automation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20improve%20performance%20and%20maintenance.%20Those%20tools%20can%20check%20and%20analyze%20uptime%2C%20latency%20in%20connections%2C%20and%20any%20use%20of%20the%205G%20connection%20to%20ensure%20that%20only%20those%20authorized%20can%20access%20it.%20Companies%20and%20enterprises%20should%20make%20sure%20to%20budget%20and%20plan%20for%20these%20technical%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusinesses-build-secure-5g-network-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698094797000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65241f846e038039826d55c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusinesses-build-secure-5g-network-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20businesses%20stand%20to%20benefit%20from%205G%2C%20but%20not%20all%20need%20it.%20To%20build%20a%20secure%205G%20network%2C%20ensure%20you%20have%20the%20right%20experts%20on%20board%20to%20manage%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Chris%20Stokel-Walker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusinesses-build-secure-5g-network-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20American%20Airlines%20passenger%20says%20he%20got%20severe%20injuries%20after%20being%20'scalded'%20by%20hot%20coffee%20during%20a%20flight%2C%20a%20lawsuit%20alleges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221422%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20American%20Airlines%20plane%3B%20George%20Latorre's%20%26quot%3Bdamaged%26quot%3B%20tattoo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6536cc7096f7540cd0635055%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20American%20Airlines%20plane%3B%20George%20Latorre's%20%26quot%3Bdamaged%26quot%3B%20tattoo.%3Cp%3ENicolas%20Economou%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20lawsuit%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ff