22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23224325%2FThe-Wire-51.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EDays%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20discussed%20the%20developments%20in%20West%20Asia%20with%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20leaders%2C%20he%20spoke%20to%20Jordan%E2%80%99s%20King%20Abdullah%20regarding%20the%20same%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%2023.%20Both%20Modi%20and%20King%20Abdullah%20called%20for%20intensive%20efforts%20towards%20an%20%E2%80%9Cearly%20resolution%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20region%20plunged%20into%20violence%20after%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20terror%20attack%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20and%20Israeli%20counter-strikes%20on%20Gaza%20have%20led%20to%20a%20death%20toll%20of%20over%205%2C000%20lives%2C%20till%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20had%20first%20spoken%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20to%20reiterate%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-reiterates-solidarity-phone-call-netanyahu-israel-hamas%5C%22%3Esolidarity%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20Israelis%20on%20October%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20engaged%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-palestine-authority-president-mahmoud-abbas-call-israel-gaza%5C%22%3Econversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Palestinian%20Authority%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20on%20October%2019%2C%20two%20days%20after%20the%20explosion%20at%20Gaza%20City%E2%80%99s%20al-Ahli%20Hospital%20had%20incited%20outrage%20in%20the%20Arab%20world.%20During%20their%20discussion%2C%20Modi%20subtly%20adjusted%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20by%20reaffirming%20its%20longstanding%20support%20for%20the%20two-state%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20regional%20leader%20that%20Modi%20spoke%20with%20on%20Monday%20(October%2023)%20was%20Jordan%E2%80%99s%20King%20Abdullah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESpoke%20with%20His%20Majesty%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKingAbdullahII%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40KingAbdullahII%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Jordan.%20Exchanged%20views%20on%20the%20developments%20in%20the%20West%20Asia%20region.%20We%20share%20concerns%20regarding%20terrorism%2C%20violence%20and%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives.%20Concerted%20efforts%20needed%20for%20early%20resolution%20of%20the%20security%20and%20humanitarian%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1716444327604359325%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20his%20tweet%2C%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20the%20first%20time%20talked%20about%20an%20end%20to%20the%20crisis%20by%20referring%20to%20%E2%80%9Cearly%20resolution%20of%20the%20security%20and%20humanitarian%20situation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20countries%20in%20the%20global%20south%2C%20India%20has%20refrained%20from%20explicitly%20advocating%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20up%20to%20this%20point.%20However%2C%20the%20mention%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Cearly%20resolution%E2%80%9D%20appeared%20to%20signify%20a%20shift%20towards%20that%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkingabdullah.jo%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fking-india-pm-discuss-means-stop-deteriorating-situation-gaza%5C%22%3EThe%20Jordanian%20government%E2%80%99s%20readout%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20talks%20said%20that%20two%20leaders%20%E2%80%9Cdiscussed%20means%20to%20stop%20the%20deteriorating%20situation%20in%20Gaza%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20press%20note%20also%20said%20that%20the%20discussions%20covered%20the%20%E2%80%9Cneed%20to%20step%20up%20international%20efforts%20to%20end%20the%20war%20on%20Gaza%2C%20protect%20civilians%20and%20hospitals%2C%20and%20guarantee%20the%20sustained%20delivery%20of%20medical%20and%20relief%20aid%20into%20the%20strip%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20Majesty%20warned%20of%20the%20deteriorating%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20the%20repercussions%20of%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20strip%20on%20the%20region%20and%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJordan%20has%20a%20direct%20interest%20in%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20issue%2C%20as%20it%20has%20custodianship%20of%20Islamic%20holy%20sites%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20including%20the%20Al-Aqsa%20mosque.%20It%20has%20played%20host%20to%20around%20three%20million%20Palestinian%20refugees%20and%20nearly%20half%20of%20its%20population%20is%20of%20Palestinian%20descent.%20Jordan%20has%20the%20longest%20border%20with%20Israel%20and%20West%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Egypt%2C%20Jordan%20was%20the%20second%20Arab%20country%20to%20sign%20a%20peace%20treaty%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20peace%20summit%20held%20in%20Cairo%20on%20Saturday%20(October%2021)%2C%20King%20Abdullah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2FThis%2520is%2520a%2520war%2520crime%2520according%2520to%2520international%2520law%2C%2520and%2520a%2520red%2520line%2520for%2520all%2520of%2520us%2C%5C%22%3Ecautioned%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20any%20measure%20to%20displace%20Palestinians%20from%20Gaza.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20war%20crime%20according%20to%20international%20law%2C%20and%20a%20red%20line%20for%20all%20of%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Jordanian%20leader%20had%20also%20asked%20the%20international%20community%20to%20criticise%20Israel%20for%20the%20targeting%20of%20civilian%20infrastructure%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20prohibition%20on%20the%20supply%20of%20fuel%2C%20food%2C%20water%2C%20and%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698081485000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23224325%2FThe