ous%20planning%2C%20networking%20and%20creativity%20is%20no%20less%20than%20a%20learning%20opportunity%20for%20any%20business%20school%20student.%20Her%20positive%20attitude%20and%20demeanour%20is%20infectious%20and%20you%20cannot%20say%20no%20to%20a%20request%20from%20Sudha%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%C2%A0A%20Kala%2C%20managing%20committee%20member%2C%20Multiple%20Sclerosis%20Society%20of%20India%20(MSSI)%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20Chapter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20though%20the%20camps%20have%20been%20discontinued%2C%20the%20students%20and%20teachers%20do%20not%20miss%20an%20opportunity%20to%20drop%20in%20and%20spend%20time%20with%20their%20mentor.%20Around%20100%20teachers%20volunteered%20at%20the%20summer%20camp%20over%20the%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Located%20at%20the%20Sudha's%20home%20in%20Malleswaram%2C%20which%20was%20thrown%20open%20to%20the%20children%2C%20the%20summer%20camp%20was%20a%20big%20hit.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22