re%20are%20sightings%20too%20close%20to%20civilisation%2C%20we%20alert%20the%20authorities%20so%20the%20animals%20can%20be%20safely%20relocated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sunando%20informs%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20sees%20the%20place%20as%20a%20home%20not%20just%20for%20himself%20but%20for%20the%20animals%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Opening%20our%20home%20to%20wildlife%20lovers%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ESunando%20shares%20that%20initially%2C%20he%20had%20no%20plans%20of%20converting%20his%20home%20into%20a%20homestay.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20moved%20into%20the%20place%20in%202011%20and%20have%20lived%20here%20ever%20since.%20Whenever%20we%20would%20host%20our%20friends%2C%20they%20would%20insist%20we%20share%20it%20with%20others%20too.%20There%20was%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20land%20on%20our%20property%20too%2C%20so%20we%20thought%20%E2%80%98Why%20not%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuTHMcIvX44%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuTHMcIvX44%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuTHMcIvX44%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Tanhau%20(%40tanhau_tales)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Sunando%20opened%20his%20home%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329902%2Fwildlife-photographer-dr-ramakanta-panda-mumbai-heart-surgeon-pictures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20enthusiasts%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20him%20who%20wish%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20wild.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20three%20huts%20besides%20our%20place%2C%20and%20we%20have%20hosted%20at%20least%20500%20people%20since%202016%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAjit%20Kumar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20visiting%20the%20place%20with%20his%20family%20for%20more%20than%20five%20years%20now%2C%20shares%20what%20it%20feels%20like%20to%20stay%20at%20Tanhau.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20is%20surreal%20and%20I%20am%20not%20exaggerating%20when%20I%20say%20that%20it%20is%20the%20best%20experience%20I%20have%20ever%20had.%20It%20is%20so%20peaceful%20and%20quiet%3B%20it%20teaches%20you%20the%20importance%20of%20slow%20living.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20that%20it%20is%20a%20very%20sustainable%20setup.%20It%20feels%20good%20to%20know%20that%20I%20am%20travelling%20and%20not%20leaving%20a%20carbon%20footprint%20behind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20teach%20my%20son%20the%20importance%20of%20preserving%20nature%20and%20this%20homestay%20was%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20do%20so.%20We%20participated%20in%20the%20project%20with%20a%20school%20near%20the%20homestay%20where%20we%20tried%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20plastic%20and%20its%20carbon%20footprint%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20promote%20slow%20and%20responsible%20travel%2C%20the%20homestay%20hosts%20unique%20activities%20to%20engage%20the%20guests.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20walking%20safaris%20in%20the%20buffer%20forest%2C%20which%20is%20an%20amazing%20and%20unique%20experience%20in%20itself.%20Of%20course%2C%20you%20can%20take%20a%20safari%20and%20sit%20in%20a%20jeep%2C%20but%20on%20a%20walking%20safari%2C%20you%20can%20observe%20nature%20and%20animals%20closely%2C%20without%20emitting%20any%20carbon.%20We%20also%20organise%20village%20walks%20and%20encourage%20our%20guests%20to%20participate%20in%20any%20ongoing%20village%20festivals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20guest%2C%20Avika%20Sood%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20silence%20in%20the%20place%20is%20rejuvenating.%20I%20found%20out%20about%20the%20homestay%20through%20a%20friend%20and%20have%20visited%20it%20a%20few%20times.%20The%20place%20is%20offbeat%20and%20unique.%20There%20is%20so%20much%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20wildlife%20and%20animal%20kingdom%2C%20and%20Sunando%20is%20a%20walking%20library%20in%20that%20sense.%20He%20is%20very%20passionate%20about%20his%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tanhau%20has%20hosted%20over%20500%20guests%20at%20their%20mud%20homestay.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1-1-1697812365-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F20