0fungal-based%20composting%20inoculum.%20In%20this%2C%20the%20solid%20and%20liquid%20waste%20is%20sandwiched%20between%20spongy%20matrixes.%20Other%20than%20moisture%2C%20the%20matrix%20also%20adsorbs%20stench%20and%20obnoxious%20gases.%20This%20provides%20for%20the%20aerobic%20condition%20when%20waste%20disintegrates%20into%20uniform%20particles%20into%20organic%20manure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20fungal-based%20inoculum%20completely%20decomposes%20all%20biodegradable%20waste%20into%20soilless%20planting%20media.%20Usually%2C%20we%20add%20100-200%20grams%20of%20compost%20with%20soil%2C%20but%20with%20this%2C%20we%20can%20convert%20thousands%20of%20kgs%20of%20waste%20into%20compost%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Manoj.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20game-changer%20for%20apartments%20struggling%20with%20waste%20disposal%20challenges.%20About%20200%20apartments%20and%20complexes%20in%20Kerala%20and%20Bengaluru%20have%20begun%20to%20dispose%20of%20their%20solid%20waste%2C%20both%20degradable%20and%20non-degradable%2C%20in%20a%20scientific%20and%20cost-effective%20way%20while%20promoting%20green%20earth.%20For%20this%2C%20Kenterra%20charges%20about%20Rs%20350%20per%20month%20per%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Manoj%20informs%20that%20they%20are%20able%20to%20manage%20about%2010%2C000%20kg%20of%20waste%20every%20day.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20http